 ('108', '108', 'en_us', 'People', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'People Passionate about Design', '<p>We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s communication&nbsp;programs. Our students work under the guidance of full-time staff members from the <a href=\"http://www.kent.edu/cci\">College of Communication of Information</a> and a <a href=\"{entry:539:url}\">professional /&nbsp;faculty&nbsp;advisory board</a>, ensuring we produce the highest quality products for our clients. &nbsp;Our commitment to real-world experience ensures our&nbsp;<a href=\"{entry:540:url}\">numerous alumni</a>&nbsp;are poised for real-world success upon graduation.</p>', 'Work for IdeaBase', 'We empower our student employees to imagine, create and deliver quality designs while gaining real-world experience on client-facing projects. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Committed to quality.', '<p>Were committed to delivering quality work to our clients. Thats why our student employees work under the guidance of our professional staff from Kent States College of Communication of Information and a professional advisory board. Our student employees interact directly with clients, developing proposals, managing projects and handling all stages of design production.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s design, advertising, user experience, computer science and electronic media programs. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-06 14:08:01', '2016-02-12 17:48:05', '2678f2c6-9572-4609-b1de-6434f12b3901'),
 ('109', '109', 'en_us', 'Services', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Design services tailored to you', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>We support our clients design initiatives from the early discovery phase through implementation (or anywhere in between). Whether youre laying the foundation for your products success, or building out and refining your design, were here to help. And we do all of this right here locally from our <a href=\"{entry:492:url}\">fabulous office space</a> in downtown Kent.<br></p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>', '<p>We can test the performance and usability of your product on various devices in our User Experience Testing Lab. This is a great resource to ensure that your product translates across all platforms.\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>While our unique business model allows us to deliver high-quality products at an affordable cost, theres no one size fits all when it comes to individual client needs. We work with our clients upfront to define goals and timelines to ensure that we deliver a great end&nbsp;product within the projects constraints. Together, well plan and build something great, and it wont break the bank.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today and we\'ll put together a customized proposal&nbsp;for your next project.&nbsp;</p>', 'Sounds great, how much does it cost?', 'More about our UX Testing Lab', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Let our suite of user research, design and testing services guide your product development; we offer everything from competitive analysis to graphic and Web design to eyetracking and usability testing in our very own UX Testing Lab.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-06 14:37:07', '2016-02-