 ('208', '213', 'en_us', 'Rachel Kozy', NULL, 'Designer', 'rkozy@ideabasekent.com', '', '<p>Rachel&nbsp;is&nbsp;a visual communication design student at Kent State University graduating in May 2016. Although she&nbsp;love all aspects of design, she&nbsp;am especially interested in visual branding, UI/UX and typography. In the past, Rachel&nbsp;has&nbsp;interned with MTV in New York City and Go Media in Cleveland, and is&nbsp;am currently the president of her&nbsp;collegiate chapter of AIGA. When Rachel is&nbsp;not designing, you\'ll likely find her&nbsp;playing video games or rewatching Avatar: The Last Airbender.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Visual Communication Design', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Kozy', 'Rachel', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-17 18:22:57', '2016-02-11 22:40:42', 'c84cf9ce-dcfc-48d9-90b2-51570cd4ae17'),
