 ('309', '314', 'en_us', 'Kent State Athletics Annual Report 2015', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>IdeaBase was brought on board for the second year in a row to develop and design Kent State University Athletics\' year-in-review/annual report.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The interactive report is designed in HTML/CSS&nbsp;and this year features a single-page design&nbsp;(with supplemental article pages). The design is composed of&nbsp;photos, text and custom icons that match the university\'s blue and gold branding.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>We went through a process of discovery, content gathering, design/architecture&nbsp;and development over a period of five&nbsp;months.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>From a technical perspective, the site utilizes:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Jekyll, a static site generator that doesn\'t require a full content management system</li><li>Grunt&nbsp;for task running, including image resizing, browser refreshing and code compiling</li><li>SASS&nbsp;for writing CSS&nbsp;for efficiency</li><li>CSS&nbsp;animations</li><li>Image and JavaScript compression and lazy loading for optimal performance</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>The site launched in September 2015.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.supportgoldenflashes.com/2015_Annual_Report/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-22 01:06:02', '2016-02-11 18:14:11', '063a4e11-fdd3-4166-bc1b-3e6e00483428'),
 ('311', '316', 'en_us', 'Callie Sullivan', NULL, 'User Experience Designer', 'csullivan@ideabasekent.com', '', '<p>Callie received her Bachelors degree in English from UW-Madison and is currently pursuing her Masters degree in User Experience Design through Kent State University, where she will graduate in August of 2016.&nbsp;She is dually employed by IdeaBase, as well as a pharmacy benefit management company called Navitus based out of Madison, Wisconsin. At Navitus, Callie works as a Marketing Analyst and is part of the organizations Web team, assisting primarily on content creation and organization for both the companys internal and external sites. works in the Marketing department of a pharmacy benefit management company called Navitus based out of Madison, Wisconsin. At IdeaBase, Callie has worked on several projects&mdash;including the State Library of Ohio redesign, the design of the ICE Consulting website, and the redesign of the IdeaBase website&mdash;as the lead Content Strategist and Information Architect.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>When Callies not eating, sleeping and breathing UX, shes pursuing her other passions, which include music, the French language, travel and cheese plates.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'B.A. English, M.S. User Experience Design Graduate Student', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Sullivan', 'Callie ', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-29 15:39:30', '2016-02-09 06:11:53', 'fd171b5e-9de7-4b06-b5da-57f31f6c186b'),
 ('312', '317', 'en_us', 'Christopher Uhler', NULL, 'User Experience Designer', 'cuhler@ideabasekent.com', '', '<p>Christopher&nbsp;is a Graduate Student at Kent State University&nbsp;studying User Experience Design and will graduate in August, 2016.&nbsp;&nbsp;He also has a B.A. in Film Studies from&nbsp;Ohio State University.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Beyond IdeaBase, Chris also works as a Production Manager at Bent Tree Coffee Roasters. In his spare time&nbsp;Chris enjoys spending time with his family, backpacking&nbsp;and photography.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'M.S. User Experience Design', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Uhler', 'Christopher', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-29 15:45:43', '2016-02-09 15:51:34', '5637eb28-4582-46e8-8b35-7dfec756366f'),
 ('313', '318', 'en_us', 'Courtney Kaminski', NULL, 'Account Manager', 'ckaminski@ideabasekent.com', '', '<p>&nbsp;Courtney is&nbsp;a senior advertising student at Kent State, graduating in May 2016. She&nbsp;is&nbsp;an account manager at IdeaBase, and&nbsp;also has&nbsp;a digital marketing internship,&nbsp;working&nbsp;for&nbsp;FedEx Office in Kent, Ohio.&nbsp;Courtney also had&nbsp;a copywriting internship, so she&nbsp;has&nbsp;plenty of writing experience!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She&nbsp;has&nbsp;eight guinea pigs and two cats, all of which are very spoiled. She&nbsp;spends&nbsp;a lot of time reading and learning about design. Courtney&nbsp;loves to cook and can usually be found searching the Web for new recipes.&nbsp;</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Advertising ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Kaminski', 'Courtney', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-29 15:47:48', '2016-02-09 15:53:42', 'e2ea185a-5dc9-4061-8a13-7776c326adaa'),
