 ('334', '339', 'en_us', 'Beyond the Beans: Life of a Coffee Roaster and User Experience Designer: Christopher Uhler', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>My name is Chris Uhler and Im a user experience designer at IdeaBase. Im also a graduate student in Kent States user experience design program.</p><p>IdeaBase has been a great opportunity for gaining real-world experience. Personally, Ive been learning a ton from my manager Chris Hallahan. He is a super awesome resource, and its truly rewarding to be able to work on a project the whole way through.</p><p>Before I started at IdeaBase in March, I actually had no idea this place even existed until my co-worker at Bent Tree Coffee Roasters told me about it. Ive been working at Bent Tree (also here in Kent) for two years as a Production Manager, but Im glad I found out about IdeaBase because its a great starting point for my future in the User Experience Design field.</p><p>My main client right now is Northeast Ohio Medical University. I am working on a competitive analysis for them in support of their future website redesign. A competitive analysis is basically the process of looking at similar websites and analyzing their strengths and weaknesses. Ive also created and sent out a survey to get feedback on the current site, and Ill be analyzing the data when the survey closes.</p><p>I stay super busy with work and school, but in my spare time I enjoy photography, home brewing, and my motorcycle. Recently, I made a Kolsch brew, which is a light, sweet beer. I think it turned out pretty well. I needed a break from the heavy stuff, and this was a nice alternative.</p><p>Right now, Im just super excited to get married in the fall. My fianc and I have been together about 5 years. We actually met at Kent State, and have been together ever since.</p><p>Overall, I am just excited for the experience at IdeaBase. I know I will be able to learn a lot here and can use this experience as a good foundation for my future.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-29 19:15:59', '2016-02-08 21:56:27', 'bb1ae383-e4a7-434d-8444-e9dc34316b22'),
