 ('341', '346', 'en_us', 'The Atmosphere of IdeaBase: Sarah Holzers Story', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Hi! My name is Sarah Holzer and Im a senior Visual Communications Design major. I started working at IdeaBase in the summer of 2015. It counted as my internship, but I will be continuing to work here throughout the fall.&nbsp;Im lucky to have a lot of friends that work at IdeaBase, which is how I heard they were hiring for the summer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are a lot of things I like about VCD, the main one being that I (obviously) get to be creative and I get to study a hobby of mine and make it a career. I also really like the community within VCD. The students in the program have become some of my best friends and its awesome to have classes with them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IdeaBase has definitely helped prepare me for my future career in graphic design. My main takeaway so far is learning how to work directly with clients. My first week here I had to present logo concepts to a client and that isnt an experience I would have learned in a classroom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If I had to choose a favorite thing about IdeaBase it would have be the sense of community. I feel pretty lucky to honestly be able to say I like every single person that I work with, and its nice to feel comfortable enough to ask for help if you need it. A lot of places can be competitive and people may be scared to ask questions, but IdeaBase is never like that. Its a very collaborative and helpful environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Beyond IdeaBase and my studies I love gardening. Im currently growing a lemon tree and an apple tree. My apartment is also filled with lots of plants. I think thats one of the best ways to make a house a home. I also really like yoga and puppies, but who doesnt love puppies!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After graduation, I plan on working at an advertising agency or design firm in Pittsburgh. I want to save some money and move to New York City, as soon as I can afford it, so I can further my career there. Hopefully soon Ill be happily working in New York with a new puppy and lots of plants!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-29 19:23:53', '2016-02-08 21:56:28', '56f2b6bd-6757-4eb1-9355-919aeda53aa8'),
