 ('348', '353', 'en_us', 'ICE Consulting Branding / Website', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>IdeaBase redesigned the Ice Consulting&nbsp;website and Glyphix (kentglyphix.org) created a new brand identity and logo for Ice Consulting&nbsp;in July&nbsp;2015. The website uses a customized template from Squarespace.com, with colors, type and custom-designed iconography that matches the new ICE identity and the content was written and positioned to match the ICE business goals and increase search optimization. The website was also designed to be responsive and scale across multiple devices.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://iceconsulting.org/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-31 16:47:36', '2016-02-04 23:33:24', '5dec23a4-0377-4465-aa12-62453d73b720'),
