 ('383', '388', 'en_us', 'Jillian Coorey', NULL, 'Assistant Professor, Visual Communication Design', '', '', '<p>Jillian Coorey is an Assistant Professor in the School of Visual Communication Design at Kent State University. Prior to coming to Kent, Jillian spent five years working in Chicago as a designer for various companies, in addition to managing freelance clientele. As a designer, she strives to create thoughtful and innovative solutions that combine conceptual and creative thinking. Jillian received her MFA in Graphic Design from the University of Illinois at Chicago and her BFA in Graphic Design from The State University of New York at Fredonia. She has also studied in Basel, Switzerland at The Basel School of Design. Her thesis research involved dance and design, creating work that challenges and informs the dimensional experience of movement, time and space.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Coorey', 'Jillian', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-05 18:59:13', '2016-01-22 18:02:13', '58ba6ab1-20ca-4b80-ade0-f1dd2b5ff560'),
