 ('389', '394', 'en_us', 'Valora Renicker', NULL, 'Assistant Professor, Visual Communication Design and Creative Director, Glyphix Design Studio', '', '', '<p>Valora received her MFA in Graphic Design from Kent State University and a BFA in Graphic Design and Art Education from the University of Akron. Her background includes experience in the design field and teaching art in the public schools. Valora is an Assistant Professor in the School of Visual Communication Design (VCD) at Kent State University where she has taught course in typography, formal and conceptual design development, 3D graphic design and computer software. She is the Creative Director of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.kent.edu/glyphix\">Glyphix</a>, an award-winning student-staffed design studio within the School of VCD, where she instructs both undergraduate and graduate level students in the real-world implementation of design practices and production.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Renicker', 'Valora', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-05 19:15:35', '2016-01-22 18:02:14', '4955de73-1174-468a-82f3-e8d1f09cb4b3'),
