 ('539', '629', 'en_us', 'Schneller: A laminates manufacturer for the transportation industry', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The IdeaBase team for this project wanted to make a&nbsp;huge impact because of Schnellers status as the top&nbsp;designer for laminates and textile flooring for the transportation&nbsp;industry. For the conference room, the team&nbsp;of designers developed a map display that personifies&nbsp;Schnellers global footprint. The team then designed a&nbsp;process gallery that illustrates the process of making&nbsp;laminates. Another dimension of this project included&nbsp;creating an image that displays a plane taking off from&nbsp;the runway. This piece is positioned directly outside&nbsp;Schnellers conference room and provides a strong&nbsp;and powerful statement for their company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The IdeaBase team also took Schnellers branding pattern&nbsp;and used it throughout its facility. The dots were applied&nbsp;on the walls to create an atmosphere that represented&nbsp;Schnellers product. The final piece of the design was for&nbsp;the lobby. This design needed to be welcoming as well&nbsp;as informative. Therefore, a gallery was developed that&nbsp;creatively framed Schellers numerous laminates.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-04 22:16:45', '2016-02-12 17:00:43', '54a02aea-6fa9-472e-95fd-7af9487066a9'),
 ('540', '630', 'en_us', 'CCI Commons Website: A living-learning community at Kent State University', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The main goal of the redesign was to portray the&nbsp;energetic and collaborative atmosphere that CCI&nbsp;Commons creates for Kent State University students.&nbsp;The new site emphasizes these qualities through&nbsp;spirited photography, colorful typography, and dynamic&nbsp;layouts. The redesign also carried over to mobile and&nbsp;desktop applications. As a result of the websites&nbsp;revamp, new students interested in CCI Commons&nbsp;have access to a great resource that helps them find&nbsp;information and gain personal perspectives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IdeaBase worked in collaboration with Chris Hallahan,&nbsp;an interactive Web designer and developer with Kent&nbsp;States University Communications and Marketing&nbsp;department. This is one of several projects that&nbsp;IdeaBase collaborated on with UCM. This relationship&nbsp;allows Glyphix and IdeaBase to ensure that their work&nbsp;is in line with the universitys brand standards and&nbsp;provides students with an insight into the in-house&nbsp;design atmosphere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College of Communication and Information&nbsp;Commons website was an extremely rewarding project&nbsp;for the individuals involved with its redesign. The lead&nbsp;designer met with CCI Commons Director Marianne&nbsp;Warzinkski to develop a deeper insight and overall&nbsp;vision for the new CCI Commons website. After&nbsp;speaking with Warzinkski, the students researched&nbsp;living and learning communities at other colleges and&nbsp;universities to determine how the site could stand&nbsp;apart. From there, the designers were trusted by the&nbsp;client to go to work with their creative freedom and&nbsp;create a website that is truly outstanding. The finished&nbsp;site design was recognized with a gold ADDY at the&nbsp;2014 Akron ADDY Awards.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-04 22:23:52', '2016-02-08 21:56:28', '8653783d-1321-45e3-9ead-140a4cb7fcef'),
