 ('793', '925', 'en_us', 'Welcome to the IdeaBase Style Guide & Stuff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '<p>The purpose of this style guide is to help IdeaBase employees create great content with consistent voice, tone, editorial and visual style.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Lets get started.</h4>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>When writing new content for IdeaBase, use this style guide to maintain consistency and brand authenticity. Weve divided the guide by topic based on the following main concepts: </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li>brand statements\r\n</li><li>voice & tone\r\n</li><li>grammar & mechanics\r\n</li><li>writing on the Web\r\n</li><li>visual design & brand elements\r\n</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Feel free to use the search feature if you know what youre looking for</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-08 20:59:37', '2016-03-17 15:19:08', '7e472777-e68e-4fca-8b85-990803eacbb0'),
