 ('86', '109', '12', '87', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"12\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Process Index\",\"slug\":\"process-index\",\"postDate\":1445610309,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"\",\"79\":\"<p>Our comprehensive service offering supports our clients\' design initiatives from the early discovery phase through implementation and on-going improvements. Whether you;re laying the foundation for your product\'s success, or building out and refining that product, we\'re here to help. Did we mention we do all of this right here locally in Kent, OH? That\'s right, we\'re minutes away from Kent State University.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"43\":\"\",\"42\":\"Our design process is tailored to you.\",\"82\":\"While our unique business model allows us to deliver high-quality products at an affordable cost, there\'s no \\\"one size fits all\\\" when it comes to individual client needs. We work with our clients upfront to define project goals and guidelines to ensure that we deliver a great end product within the project\'s constraints. Together, we\'ll build something great, and it won\'t break the bank. Don\'t believe us? Just as our clients:\",\"81\":\"Sounds great, how much does it cost?\",\"80\":\"<p>*We can test the performance and usability of your product on various devices in our <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.google.com\\\">User Experience Testing Lab.<\\/a> This is a great resource to ensure that your product translates across all platforms.\\r\\n<\\/p>\"}}', '2015-11-17 15:29:48', '2015-11-17 15:29:48', 'c10a5db4-4088-4302-90ae-c0aa0e15c1ec'),
