 ('286', '398', '4', '87', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Schneller AerFilm Flex Product Demonstration Video\",\"slug\":\"schneller-aerfilm-flex-product-demonstration-video\",\"postDate\":1452024840,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"48\":\"\",\"117\":[\"397\"],\"61\":[\"326\"],\"9\":\"<p>IdeaBase filmed and edited this&nbsp;product demonstration video for use in tradeshows by Schneller, a manufacturer of custom, specialty laminates and coated fabrics for transportation interiors in Kent, OH.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>AerFilm Flex\\u00ae is Schneller\\u2019s&nbsp;newest decorative laminate, designed to provide superior formability compared to established decorative laminates. Engineered to cover complex, compound-curve, 3 dimensional parts, AerFilm Flex\\u00ae is lightweight and provides superior texture retention while providing the design freedom needed to create premium cabin designs.<\\/p>\",\"46\":\"\",\"88\":[\"180\"],\"104\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=5GQs1SARyro\"}}', '2016-01-12 17:19:46', '2016-01-12 17:19:46', '9f64289d-5521-4e74-af34-c0cb6c14c650'),
 ('287', '403', '4', '87', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"IdeaBase: Powered by Kent State Students\",\"slug\":\"ideabase-powered-by-kent-state-students\",\"postDate\":1452027540,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"48\":\"\",\"117\":[\"402\"],\"61\":[\"320\",\"326\",\"146\"],\"9\":\"<p>Students and staff at IdeaBase speak about their experiences working on real-world client projects. Directed, edited and filmed exclusively by students at IdeaBase, the video shows how students from various backgrounds put into action what they\\u2019ve learned in their Kent State University classes. IdeaBase is a student-run creative agency in downtown Kent and is a service of the College of Communication and Information.<\\/p>\",\"46\":\"\",\"88\":[\"180\"],\"104\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI\"}}', '2016-01-12 17:20:16', '2016-01-12 17:20:16', '7609c029-d90b-430e-94fe-b24e44e0fd70'),
 ('288', '365', '4', '87', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Florence Tour: Kent State College of Communication and Information\",\"slug\":\"florence-tour-kent-state-college-of-communication-and-information\",\"postDate\":1451581860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"48\":\"\",\"117\":[\"373\"],\"61\":[\"149\"],\"9\":\"<p>The Florence Alumni & Friends Tour campaign was developed for Kent State\'s College of Communication and Information with the goal of promoting an exclusive trip to Florence, Italy for alumni of the college. IdeaBase designers created a custom design system that was used across many different printed and digital pieces.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The campaign included:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>A printed book, explaining the benefits of attending the trip<\\/li><li>A folded invitation, mailed to CCI alumni<\\/li><li>A website, to which those interested were directed for more information<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Florence Tour campaign won a Solver ADDY&nbsp;from the Akron Advertising Federation in February 2015 as part&nbsp;of the professional Campaign category.<\\/p>\",\"46\":[\"364\"],\"88\":[\"178\",\"179\"],\"104\":\"\"}}', '2016-01-12 17:23:24', '2016-01-12 17:23:24', '3122295d-6a61-4b64-85c0-6cada530ab6e'),
