 ('402', '147', '3', '204', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Victoria Ripepi\",\"slug\":\"victoria-ripepi\",\"postDate\":1446762360,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>My name is Victoria Ripepi and I am a 5th year senior graduating in May 2016 with a major in Communication Studies, concentration interpersonal. I\'m from Hudson, OH and came to Kent State because I am the oldest of 6 kids and didn\'t want to be far away from home. After being here for 5 years, I am very ready to move onto the next chapter of my life and begin finding a job out of Ohio. I am the event coordinator at IdeaBase and helped successfully plan over a 100 person Open House in the Fall of 2015. Now I will be joining IdeaBase this Spring 2016 as an Account Manager and I\'m very excited for that. I hope to get a job in corporate event planning and\\/or an experience marketing firm. Previous to working at IdeaBase, I worked for a small event planning company that put on 100 vendor art and craft shows throughout Northeast Ohio and the Columbus area. I am a people person and I always have a smile on my face. I have 2 cats, my favorite color is black and my favorite food is fried pickles.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Communication Studies and Interpersonal concentration\",\"4\":\"vripepi@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Victoria\",\"7\":\"\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Event Coordinator\",\"114\":\"Ripepi\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"307\"],\"89\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Linkedin\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/victoriaripepi\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"\",\"staffSocLink\":\"\"}}}}}', '2016-01-26 15:05:06', '2016-01-26 15:05:06', '4646234e-7730-4396-a07f-9be14999ff75'),
