 ('472', '492', '14', '204', 'en_us', '17', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"WHO WE ARE\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1453394220,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoURL\":\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/VqQZbh8P8AI\",\"videoCaption\":\" In this IdeaBase student-produced video, our students talk about their experiences working at IdeaBase.\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>IN THE HEART OF DOWNTOWN KENT<\\/h2><p>Our office space&mdash;conveniently located in Downtown Kent&mdash;features an open layout with a conference room, creative workspace, educational area and UX Testing Lab; it\\u2019s a great space for collaboration for students and clients alike!<br><\\/p>\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Visit us today!\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":\"\"}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>A LEGACY OF STUDENT-LED DESIGN SOLUTIONS<\\/h2><p>Formerly the Tannery, IdeaBase opened in 2009 as the brainchild of Jim Gaudino, the founding dean of the College of Communication and Information (CCI). Gaudino worked with the directors from each of the CCI schools to develop a vision for a student-staffed organization where students could receive hands-on experience. &nbsp;<br>In 2014, to better reflect its core mission of providing unique educational experiences while delivering quality design solutions, the Tannery transformed into IdeaBase. Within the same year, IdeaBase expanded its service offering with the addition of Glyphix, a classroom studio experience from the School of Visual Communication Design. IdeaBase continues to operate as part of the CCI, always evolving to bring new services and experiences to the university community and beyond.<\\/p>\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Learn More About Our Team\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":[\"108\"]}}},\"148\":\"IdeaBase is an awesome design agency and that\'s all you need to know.\",\"37\":[\"489\"],\"135\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we bridge the gap between classroom and career by bringing together top-performing Kent State students to tackle real-world client problems. Our team represents a variety of backgrounds, including Visual Communication Design, Public Relations, Advertising, Computer Information Systems, Digital Sciences, Marketing and Communication Studies students. <br>Thanks to the diverse talent of our student employees, we offer a comprehensive service offering that includes advertising, branding, copywriting, identity design, marketing research, web design, usability studies, environmental design services and <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/process#entry:109\\\">much more<\\/a>. As part of a thriving university community, we also have access to additional resources to enhance our suite of services.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-26 16:48:34', '2016-01-26 16:48:34', 'a9c81661-c0aa-4942-802e-35e6e03d0456'),
 ('473', '515', '14', '150', 'en_us', '21', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"User Experience Testing Lab\",\"slug\":\"ux\",\"postDate\":1453822920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"523\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h1>Just a few of our services include:<\\/h1>\"}},\"517\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Eye Tracking Usability<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer both traditional desktop eye tracking as well as wearable eyetracking technologies from Tobii. Eye tracking allows our user experience designers to closely study your product to see exactly where users are (and aren\\u2019t) looking. Using this measurable data, we\\u2019re able to suggest user experience improvements that help your users complete their goals faster and easier. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our eye tracking software can produce stunning visualizations, including heat maps and gaze plots, to help you communicate your findings to your stakeholders. It\\u2019s also a great tool for academic research. In fact, IdeaBase was featured in a national study on multimedia journalism by the Reynolds Journalism Institute.<\\/p>\"}},\"521\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Introducing Tobii Glasses 2<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/Images\\/basic\\/Screen-Shot-2016-01-21-at-11.25.32-AM.png#asset:491:url\\\" alt=\\\"Introducing Tobii Glasses 2\\\" title=\\\"Introducing Tobii Glasses 2\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<figcaption>For the first time, we\\u2019re able to accurately conduct testing on mobile devices, including phones and tablets, and environmental designs, such as store displays and product packaging using the state of the art Tobii Glasses 2.<\\/figcaption>\"}},\"518\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>In-Person and Remote Usability Testing<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer task-based usability studies that are conducted in-person by our research team. &nbsp;We\\u2019re also able to conduct remote user research using a variety of online tools. &nbsp;Our team can assist with recruiting, writing testing scripts and analyzing testing results.<\\/p>\"}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Open Device Lab<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With a variety of mobile devices on the market, it\\u2019s critical that your website or app translates across platforms and offers a consistent user experience. That\\u2019s where our Open Device Lab comes in. &nbsp;With onsite access to over 20 of the most popular devices (and expanding), our lab is a great place to test for bugs and implement fixes.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Partnering with Open Device Lab, any clients can now schedule a time to use our device lab at no charge!<\\/p>\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Donate a Device\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/opendevicelab.com\\/DYDD\"}}},\"148\":\"\",\"37\":[\"449\"],\"135\":\"<p>We proudly manage our own in-house User Experience Testing Lab. This on-site lab complements our design services by offering clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. Through this testing process, we can take the next steps in improving new or existing designs.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The lab is operated by an experienced User Experience Designer and a team of graduate students from Kent State\\u2019s renowned User Experience Design master\\u2019s program. &nbsp;<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-26 16:48:36', '2016-01-26 16:48:36', 'e5d02bd5-024d-413f-a25b-9f2e597516d5'),
 ('474', '492', '14', '204', 'en_us', '18', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"WHO WE ARE\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1453394220,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"533\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoURL\":\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/VqQZbh8P8AI\",\"videoCaption\":\" In this IdeaBase student-produced video, our students talk about their experiences working at IdeaBase.\"}},\"534\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>IN THE HEART OF DOWNTOWN KENT<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our office space&mdash;conveniently located in Downtown Kent&mdash;features an open layout with a conference room, creative workspace, educational area and UX Testing Lab; it\\u2019s a great space for collaboration for students and clients alike!<br><\\/p><p><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/Images\\/basic\\/Screen-Shot-2016-01-26-at-11.51.08-AM.png#asset:538\\\"><br><\\/p>\"}},\"535\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Visit us today!\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":\"\"}},\"536\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>A LEGACY OF STUDENT-LED DESIGN SOLUTIONS<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Formerly the Tannery, IdeaBase opened in 2009 as the brainchild of Jim Gaudino, the founding dean of the College of Communication and Information (CCI). Gaudino worked with the directors from each of the CCI schools to develop a vision for a student-staffed organization where students could receive hands-on experience. &nbsp;<br>In 2014, to better reflect its core mission of providing unique educational experiences while delivering quality design solutions, the Tannery transformed into IdeaBase. Within the same year, IdeaBase expanded its service offering with the addition of Glyphix, a classroom studio experience from the School of Visual Communication Design. IdeaBase continues to operate as part of the CCI, always evolving to bring new services and experiences to the university community and beyond.<\\/p>\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Learn More About Our Team\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":[\"108\"]}}},\"148\":\"IdeaBase is an awesome design agency and that\'s all you need to know.\",\"37\":[\"489\"],\"135\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we bridge the gap between classroom and career by bringing together top-performing Kent State students to tackle real-world client problems. Our team represents a variety of backgrounds, including Visual Communication Design, Public Relations, Advertising, Computer Information Systems, Digital Sciences, Marketing and Communication Studies students. <br>Thanks to the diverse talent of our student employees, we offer a comprehensive service offering that includes advertising, branding, copywriting, identity design, marketing research, web design, usability studies, environmental design services and <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/process#entry:109:url\\\">much more<\\/a>. As part of a thriving university community, we also have access to additional resources to enhance our suite of services.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-26 16:51:32', '2016-01-26 16:51:32', '6f0b8cfc-82ff-4ede-be4e-83f424e52c32'),
 ('475', '2', '1', '150', 'en_us', '21', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Home\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1442581332,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"36\":\"<p>We\\u2019re a Kent State student-powered design agency located in downtown Kent, Ohio. Our team represents a variety of backgrounds and disciplines, united in our passion for creating meaningful solutions for our clients.<\\/p>\",\"111\":[\"259\"],\"66\":\"Our design process is tailored to you\",\"37\":[\"260\"],\"35\":\"Research-based, student-powered design solutions\",\"141\":\"<p>http:\\/\\/www.google.com<\\/p>\",\"140\":\"Meet The IdeaBase Team\",\"139\":\"<p>We&nbsp;only hire&nbsp;the best students and staff members to work with nationally-known client partners on real-world, award-winning projects. Here are just a few of them.<\\/p>\",\"138\":\"Real Clients, Real Experience\",\"136\":{\"478\":{\"type\":\"homeProjects\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"projectImageLogo\":[\"470\"]}}},\"68\":\"<p>Our processes deliver results. No matter the industry or design challenge, our past work speaks for itself.<\\/p>\",\"67\":\"Tried-and-True\"}}', '2016-01-26 19:14:17', '2016-01-26 19:14:17', '7318c5eb-b31d-4f98-8849-133e50f54e59'),
 ('476', '109', '12', '150', 'en_us', '19', '', '{\"typeId\":\"12\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Services\",\"slug\":\"process-index\",\"postDate\":1445610309,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"148\":\"\",\"37\":[\"260\"],\"106\":\"<p>While our unique business model allows us to deliver high-quality products at an affordable cost, there\\u2019s no \\u201cone size fits all\\u201d when it comes to individual client needs. We work with our clients upfront to define goals and timelines to ensure that we deliver a great end-product within the project\\u2019s constraints. Together, we\\u2019ll plan and build something great, and it won\\u2019t break the bank.<\\/p>\",\"107\":\"Sounds great, how much does it cost?\",\"79\":\"<p>We support our clients\\u2019 design initiatives from the early discovery phase through implementation (or anywhere in between). Whether you\\u2019re laying the foundation for your product\\u2019s success, or building out and refining your design, we\\u2019re here to help. And we do all of this right here locally from our fabulous office space in downtown Kent.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"42\":\"Our design services are tailored to you\",\"94\":{\"183\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Discover\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Discover who your users are and what they are looking for in your product.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"User Interviews\"},{\"col1\":\"Surveys\"},{\"col1\":\"Competitive Analysis\"},{\"col1\":\"Persona Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Focus Groups\"},{\"col1\":\"Heuristics \"}],\"icon1\":[\"252\"],\"icon2\":[\"253\"],\"icon3\":[\"248\"],\"icon4\":[\"257\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"245\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our targeted user research methods empower you to more effectively address your users\'&nbsp;needs.<\\/p>\"}},\"184\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Design\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Design a creative product that delivers on user and business needs.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"Print & Graphic Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Video Production\"},{\"col1\":\"Email Marketing\"},{\"col1\":\"Web Design & Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Content Strategy\"},{\"col1\":\"Environmental Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Brand Identity \"},{\"col1\":\"Social Media Campaigns\"}],\"icon1\":[\"249\"],\"icon2\":[\"254\"],\"icon3\":[\"256\"],\"icon4\":[\"246\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"244\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our design strategies, whether through print, video or web, deliver custom solutions that&nbsp;promote both business and customer needs.<\\/p>\"}},\"185\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Refine\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Refine an existing product with our advanced testing process.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"In-Person Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Remote Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Device & Performance Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Eyetracking Usability \"}],\"icon1\":[\"247\"],\"icon2\":[\"250\"],\"icon3\":[\"251\"],\"icon4\":[\"255\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"258\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our advanced usability testing tools, including eye tracking, allow you to evaluate the effectiveness of design solutions.<\\/p>\"}}},\"108\":\"More about our UX Testing Lab\",\"80\":\"<p>We can test the performance and usability of your product on various devices in our User Experience Testing Lab. This is a great resource to ensure that your product translates across all platforms.\\r\\n<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-26 19:16:29', '2016-01-26 19:16:29', '79823623-b6ee-4f3e-b0c2-59f39856ffc0'),
 ('477', '108', '11', '150', 'en_us', '16', '', '{\"typeId\":\"11\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"People\",\"slug\":\"staff-profile-index\",\"postDate\":1445610228,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"39\":\"<p>We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s design, advertising, user experience, computer science, electronic media programs. Our students work under the guidance of full-time staff members from the College of Communication of Information and a&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/dev\\/prototype\\/templates\\/people.php#\\\">professional advisory board<\\/a>, ensuring we produce the highest quality products for our clients.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"This would be the description for the people page.\",\"37\":[\"260\"],\"38\":\"Our People are Passionate about Design\",\"45\":\"\",\"41\":\"We empower our student employees to imagine, create and deliver quality designs while gaining real-world experience on client-facing projects. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.\",\"58\":\"Work for IdeaBase\",\"40\":\"Work for IdeaBase\"}}', '2016-01-26 19:16:43', '2016-01-26 19:16:43', 'ee09772a-862f-4588-8beb-327f1a79f04f'),
 ('478', '148', '15', '150', 'en_us', '15', '', '{\"typeId\":\"15\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Work\",\"slug\":\"projects-homepage\",\"postDate\":1446820468,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"71\":\"How we\'re making a difference\",\"72\":\"<p>We make a positive impact on your design and our student designers by taking the time to build right. Read case studies from our past projects to see for yourself.<\\/p>\",\"109\":\"IdeaBase Classroom Experiences\",\"74\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we want our student employees to succeed. That\\u2019s why we partner with Glyphix to teach the next generation through studio experiences. Our students develop and exercise project-based skills in marketing, design, research and more. Additionally, our Responsive Web Design class ensures the next generation of designers and developers understand how to create highly functional and usable websites.<\\/p>\",\"73\":\"Helping our students succeed\",\"148\":\"\",\"37\":[\"501\"],\"110\":\"See all projects\",\"69\":\"Our Past Work Speaks for Itself\",\"70\":\"<p>We deliver awarding-winning, quality design solutions that transform our clients\\u2019 products and brands. In turn, our talented students get the chance to work directly with clients, developing proposals, managing projects and handling all stages of design production.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-26 19:16:53', '2016-01-26 19:16:53', '7e517e4a-8e6b-41c4-b85c-322c1588634d'),
