 ('497', '515', '14', '456', 'en_us', '22', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"User Experience Testing Lab\",\"slug\":\"ux\",\"postDate\":1453822920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"523\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h1>Just a few of our services include:<\\/h1>\"}},\"517\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Eye Tracking Usability<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer both traditional desktop eye tracking as well as wearable eyetracking technologies from Tobii. Eye tracking allows our user experience designers to closely study your product to see exactly where users are (and aren\\u2019t) looking. Using this measurable data, we\\u2019re able to suggest user experience improvements that help your users complete their goals faster and easier. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our eye tracking software can produce stunning visualizations, including heat maps and gaze plots, to help you communicate your findings to your stakeholders. It\\u2019s also a great tool for academic research. In fact, IdeaBase was featured in a national study on multimedia journalism by the Reynolds Journalism Institute.<\\/p>\"}},\"521\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Introducing Tobii Glasses 2<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/Images\\/basic\\/Screen-Shot-2016-01-21-at-11.25.32-AM.png#asset:491:url\\\" alt=\\\"Introducing Tobii Glasses 2\\\" title=\\\"Introducing Tobii Glasses 2\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<figcaption>For the first time, we\\u2019re able to accurately conduct testing on mobile devices, including phones and tablets, and environmental designs, such as store displays and product packaging using the state of the art Tobii Glasses 2.<\\/figcaption>\"}},\"518\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>In-Person and Remote Usability Testing<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer task-based usability studies that are conducted in-person by our research team. &nbsp;We\\u2019re also able to conduct remote user research using a variety of online tools. &nbsp;Our team can assist with recruiting, writing testing scripts and analyzing testing results.<\\/p>\"}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Open Device Lab<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With a variety of mobile devices on the market, it\\u2019s critical that your website or app translates across platforms and offers a consistent user experience. That\\u2019s where our Open Device Lab comes in. &nbsp;With onsite access to over 20 of the most popular devices (and expanding), our lab is a great place to test for bugs and implement fixes.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Partnering with Open Device Lab, any clients can now schedule a time to use our device lab at no charge!<\\/p>\"}},\"537\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Donate a Device\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/opendevicelab.com\\/DYDD\"}}},\"148\":\"Our on-site UX Testing Lab offers clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. We offer usability testing, Tobii eyetracking, and testing across a variety of mobile devices to ensure cross-platform functionality.\",\"37\":[\"449\"],\"135\":\"<p>We proudly manage our own in-house User Experience Testing Lab. This on-site lab complements our design services by offering clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. Through this testing process, we can take the next steps in improving new or existing designs.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The lab is operated by an experienced User Experience Designer and a team of graduate students from Kent State\\u2019s renowned User Experience Design master\\u2019s program. &nbsp;<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-28 02:57:43', '2016-01-28 02:57:43', 'd20667a5-f846-4a2d-b5bd-e14a5c3d5e64'),
 ('498', '492', '14', '456', 'en_us', '19', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"WHO WE ARE\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1453394220,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"533\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoURL\":\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/VqQZbh8P8AI\",\"videoCaption\":\" In this IdeaBase student-produced video, our students talk about their experiences working at IdeaBase.\"}},\"534\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>IN THE HEART OF DOWNTOWN KENT<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our office space&mdash;conveniently located in Downtown Kent&mdash;features an open layout with a conference room, creative workspace, educational area and UX Testing Lab; it\\u2019s a great space for collaboration for students and clients alike!<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/Images\\/basic\\/Screen-Shot-2016-01-26-at-11.51.08-AM.png#asset:538:url\\\"><br><\\/p>\"}},\"535\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Visit us today!\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":\"\"}},\"536\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>A LEGACY OF STUDENT-LED DESIGN SOLUTIONS<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Formerly the Tannery, IdeaBase opened in 2009 as the brainchild of Jim Gaudino, the founding dean of the College of Communication and Information (CCI). Gaudino worked with the directors from each of the CCI schools to develop a vision for a student-staffed organization where students could receive hands-on experience. &nbsp;<br>In 2014, to better reflect its core mission of providing unique educational experiences while delivering quality design solutions, the Tannery transformed into IdeaBase. Within the same year, IdeaBase expanded its service offering with the addition of Glyphix, a classroom studio experience from the School of Visual Communication Design. IdeaBase continues to operate as part of the CCI, always evolving to bring new services and experiences to the university community and beyond.<\\/p>\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Learn More About Our Team\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":[\"108\"]}}},\"148\":\"Located in Downtown Kent, OH, IdeaBase is a student-powered design agency that bridges the gap between classroom and career. IdeaBase brings together top-performing Kent State students with unique backgrounds to tackle real-world client problems. \",\"37\":[\"489\"],\"135\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we bridge the gap between classroom and career by bringing together top-performing Kent State students to tackle real-world client problems. Our team represents a variety of backgrounds, including Visual Communication Design, Public Relations, Advertising, Computer Information Systems, Digital Sciences, Marketing and Communication Studies students. <br>Thanks to the diverse talent of our student employees, we offer a comprehensive service offering that includes advertising, branding, copywriting, identity design, marketing research, web design, usability studies, environmental design services and <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/services#entry:109:url\\\">much more<\\/a>. As part of a thriving university community, we also have access to additional resources to enhance our suite of services.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-28 03:05:25', '2016-01-28 03:05:25', '6a224e35-94d0-49c7-b481-45b2948e1b80'),
 ('499', '524', '14', '456', 'en_us', '24', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Put Your Design Skills to the Test\",\"slug\":\"jobs\",\"postDate\":1453825080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"525\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Our student employees are:<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Part-time or full-time Kent State University students<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Taking at least 6 credit hours<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Who are passionate about design<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/Images\\/basic\\/Screen-Shot-2016-01-26-at-11.40.23-AM.png#asset:531:url\\\"><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Our students are primarily from the College of Communication and Information, but we have team members from other majors as well. &nbsp;Some of our past student majors include:<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nVisual Communication Design<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Communication Studies<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Advertising<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Public Relations<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Journalism<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Computer Information Systems<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Computer Science<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>User Experience Design<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Library & Information Science<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Digital Sciences<\\/p>\"}},\"530\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Think you\\u2019ll be a great fit?<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Email your resume to <a href=\\\"mailto:info@ideabasekent.com\\\">info@ideabasekent.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Not a student? Not a problem--you can still get involved by mentoring students, donating supplies or joining our professional advisory board. <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/people\\/kristin-dowling#entry:119:url\\\">Contact Kristin Dowling<\\/a>, Business Development Manager, today.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\"}}},\"148\":\"If you\'re a Kent State student who\'s passionate about design, we\'ve got a job for you. Primarily from the College of Communication and Information, our student employees have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating. \",\"37\":[\"526\"],\"135\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we believe that all students should have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating. Our student employees come from a variety of backgrounds and benefit from our comprehensive service offering.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-28 03:11:38', '2016-01-28 03:11:38', 'ef395bd7-f557-4252-86c5-cdad083e68cd'),
