 ('543', '515', '14', '456', 'en_us', '28', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"User Experience Testing Lab\",\"slug\":\"ux\",\"postDate\":1453822920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"523\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h1>Just a few of our services include:<\\/h1>\"}},\"517\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Eye Tracking Usability<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer both traditional desktop eye tracking as well as wearable eyetracking technologies from Tobii. Eye tracking allows our user experience designers to closely study your product to see exactly where users are (and aren\\u2019t) looking. Using this measurable data, we\\u2019re able to suggest user experience improvements that help your users complete their goals faster and easier. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our eye tracking software can produce stunning visualizations, including heat maps and gaze plots, to help you communicate your findings to your stakeholders. It\\u2019s also a great tool for academic research. In fact, IdeaBase was featured in a national study on multimedia journalism by the Reynolds Journalism Institute.<\\/p>\"}},\"553\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Introducing Tobii Glasses 2<\\/h2>\"}},\"552\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"564\"]}},\"518\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>In-Person and Remote Usability Testing<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer task-based usability studies that are conducted in-person by our research team. &nbsp;We\\u2019re also able to conduct remote user research using a variety of online tools. &nbsp;Our team can assist with recruiting, writing testing scripts and analyzing testing results.<\\/p>\"}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Open Device Lab<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With a variety of mobile devices on the market, it\\u2019s critical that your website or app translates across platforms and offers a consistent user experience. That\\u2019s where our Open Device Lab comes in. &nbsp;With onsite access to over 20 of the most popular devices (and expanding), our lab is a great place to test for bugs and implement fixes.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Partnering with Open Device Lab, any clients can now schedule a time to use our device lab at no charge!<\\/p>\"}},\"537\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Donate a Device\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/opendevicelab.com\\/DYDD\"}}},\"148\":\"Our on-site UX Testing Lab offers clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. We offer usability testing, Tobii eyetracking, and testing across a variety of mobile devices to ensure cross-platform functionality.\",\"37\":[\"449\"],\"135\":\"<p>We proudly manage our own in-house User Experience Testing Lab. This on-site lab complements our design services by offering clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. Through this testing process, we can take the next steps in improving new or existing designs.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The lab is operated by an experienced User Experience Designer and a team of graduate students from Kent State\\u2019s renowned User Experience Design master\\u2019s program. &nbsp;<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-29 03:53:39', '2016-01-29 03:53:39', '6a1b4185-daa8-4ff0-ba0a-c85de253ecaf'),
 ('544', '524', '14', '456', 'en_us', '31', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Put Your Design Skills to the Test\",\"slug\":\"jobs\",\"postDate\":1453825080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"554\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"531\"]}},\"525\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Our student employees are:<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Part-time or full-time Kent State University students<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Taking at least 6 credit hours<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Who are passionate about design<\\/p>\"}},\"555\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Our students are primarily from the College of Communication and Information, but we have team members from other majors as well. &nbsp;Some of our past student majors include:<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Visual Communication<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p> Design<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Communication Studies<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Advertising<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Public Relations<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Journalism<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Computer Information Systems<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Computer Science<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>User Experience Design<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Library & Information Science<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Digital Sciences<\\/p>\"}},\"530\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Think you\\u2019ll be a great fit?<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Email your resume to <a href=\\\"mailto:info@ideabasekent.com\\\">info@ideabasekent.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Not a student? Not a problem--you can still get involved by mentoring students, donating supplies or joining our professional advisory board. <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/people\\/kristin-dowling#entry:119:url\\\">Contact Kristin Dowling<\\/a>, Business Development Manager, today.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\"}}},\"148\":\"If you\'re a Kent State student who\'s passionate about design, we\'ve got a job for you. Our student employees--who are primarily from the College of Communication and Information--have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating. \",\"37\":[\"526\"],\"135\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we believe that all students should have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating. Our student employees come from a variety of backgrounds and benefit from our comprehensive service offering.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-29 03:55:16', '2016-01-29 03:55:16', 'b9bdf2a6-b811-4718-8cb3-e1527fe07b8b'),
 ('545', '557', '14', '456', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Directions and Parking\",\"slug\":\"directions\",\"postDate\":1453995060,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"558\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Once You\'ve Arrived<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Feel free to use either of our two entrances. Once you\\u2019ve arrived, go up the stairs or take the elevator to the second floor and you\\u2019ll find our office.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Front entrance is next to 4 Cats Art Studio<\\/li><li>Back entrance is behind Tree City Coffee and beside Flashers Cleaners&nbsp;<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"561\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"560\"]}},\"562\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3>Parking Options<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol><li>E. Main Street (front entrance) &nbsp;Metered Parking<\\/li><li>Erie Street (back entrance). &nbsp;Metered Parking<\\/li><li>Hourly parking is available in the PARTA parking garage<\\/li><li>On W. Main St. bridge that crosses the river (2 hour increments)<\\/li><li>Lot behind the Kent State (Columbus Street) in two hour increments (Free)<\\/li><li>Franklin Ave has (Free) parking available, near Rt. 59 overpass<\\/li><li>Lot on the corner of W.&nbsp;College Ave. and Franklin Ave.&nbsp;<\\/li><li>Large lot behind Panini\'s (free on weekend and weekdays after 5 p.m. only)<\\/li><\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>All metered parking is free on weekdays after 5 p.m. and all day on weekends.&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Parking is most difficult during lunch hours and close to 5 p.m.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you are parking on the Kent State campus, we\'re about a 10 minute walk down the Lefton Esplanade.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Need help finding our office? Give us a call at 330-672-7300.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\"}}},\"148\":\"Visit us today at our downtown Kent, OH office conveniently located in Acorn Alley at 138 E. Main Street in Suite 203. Parking options include metered parking, open lot or parking on the Kent State campus.  \",\"37\":[\"556\"],\"135\":\"<p>Planning to visit? Stop by our Downtown Kent location, conveniently located in Acorn Alley located at 138 E. Main Street in Suite 203.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-01-29 04:03:50', '2016-01-29 04:03:50', '192bf435-9383-46c8-91ba-2b583b9e4256'),
