 ('578', '314', '4', '205', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Kent State Athletics Annual Report 2015\",\"slug\":\"kent-state-athletics-annual-report-2015\",\"postDate\":1441771200,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"395\"],\"61\":[\"120\",\"320\",\"236\",\"315\",\"323\",\"146\"],\"9\":\"<p>IdeaBase was brough on board for the second year in a row to develop and design Kent State University Athletics\' year-in-review\\/annual report.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The interactive report is designed in HTML\\/CSS&nbsp;and this year features a single-page design&nbsp;(with supplemental article pages). The design is composed to photos, text and custom icons that match the university\'s blue and gold branding.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We went through a process of discovert, content gathering, design\\/architerture and development over a period of 5 months.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>From a technical perspective, the site utilizes:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Jekyll, a static site generator that doesn\'t require a full content management system<\\/li><li>Grunt, for task running, including image resizing, browser refreshing and code compiling<\\/li><li>SASS&nbsp;for writing CSS&nbsp;for efficiency<\\/li><li>CSS&nbsp;animations<\\/li><li>Image and JavaScript compression and lazy loading for optimal performance<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The site launched in September 2015.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"311\"],\"88\":[\"175\"],\"104\":\"http:\\/\\/www.supportgoldenflashes.com\\/2015_Annual_Report\\/\"}}', '2016-02-02 21:11:02', '2016-02-02 21:11:02', 'a190aca9-055b-4b06-85ad-0be3e8d91c13'),
 ('579', '355', '4', '205', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"School of Library & Information Science\",\"slug\":\"school-of-library-information-science\",\"postDate\":1451580660,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"400\"],\"61\":[\"120\",\"146\",\"423\",\"435\",\"442\"],\"9\":\"<p>IdeaBase took on the research, design and development for the School of Library & Information Science over a 9 month period, launching in January 2015.&nbsp;The website features a custom, responsive design template, research-backed content and navigation and was built in Drupal according to Kent State University\\u2019s web standards.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"354\"],\"88\":[\"177\",\"179\",\"175\"],\"104\":\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/slis\"}}', '2016-02-02 21:15:12', '2016-02-02 21:15:12', '8a81c34f-b5ba-4966-b1fe-3f7154bce0ad'),
