 ('584', '108', '11', '205', 'en_us', '23', '', '{\"typeId\":\"11\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"People\",\"slug\":\"staff-profile-index\",\"postDate\":1445610228,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"567\"],\"39\":\"<p>We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s design, advertising, user experience, computer science and&nbsp;electronic media programs. Our students work under the guidance of full-time staff members from the College of Communication of Information and a <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/people\\/board#entry:539:url\\\">professional\\/faculty&nbsp;advisory board<\\/a>, ensuring we produce the highest quality products for our clients and <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/people\\/alumni#entry:540:url\\\">numerous alumni<\\/a> who are poised for real-world success.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s design, advertising, user experience, computer science and electronic media programs. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.\",\"37\":[\"588\"],\"38\":\"Our People are Passionate about Design\",\"45\":\"\",\"41\":\"We empower our student employees to imagine, create and deliver quality designs while gaining real-world experience on client-facing projects. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.\",\"58\":\"Work for IdeaBase\",\"40\":\"Work for IdeaBase\"}}', '2016-02-02 21:36:06', '2016-02-02 21:36:06', '5f448a25-fc97-4917-958f-85ec3dfe948f'),
