 ('596', '532', '14', '150', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Classroom Experiences\",\"slug\":\"classes\",\"postDate\":1453826640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"547\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Glyphix<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>As the&nbsp;most renowned&nbsp;member of the IdeaBase family and one of the first programs of its kind, <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/glyphix\\\">Glyphix<\\/a> offers student designers the opportunity to develop creative solutions for real-world design projects. As a Glyphix designer, students gain course credits toward graduation, as well as valuable experience in teamwork, design generation and client engagement. Glyphix is located in Downtown Kent and is part of the School of Visual Communication Design. &nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"549\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"526\"]}},\"544\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Learn more about Glyphix\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/glyphix\"}},\"545\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Responsive Web Design&nbsp;Courses & Workshops<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Designed with the goal of bringing together students from multiple disciplines from within the <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/cci\\\">College of Communication and Information<\\/a>, the Responsive Web Design (RWD) courses offered through Kent State give students the skills they need to become web designers. Hands-on classes encourage active learning, and course material is constantly evolving, integrating the latest advancements in design, development and user experience design.<\\/p>\"}},\"550\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"548\"]}},\"546\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Learn more about RWD\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/rwdkent.com\\/\"}}},\"148\":\"Enhance your educational experience. Take advantage of additional hands-on learning opportunities available through our partnership with Glyphix, and our Responsive Web Design classes and workshops. \",\"37\":[\"527\"],\"135\":\"<p>Enhance your educational experience. Take advantage of additional hands-on learning opportunities available through our partnership with Glyphix, and our Responsive Web Design classes and workshops.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-04 16:50:52', '2016-02-04 16:50:52', 'bd93982d-42b6-48f6-929f-939ddc285d83'),
 ('597', '524', '14', '150', 'en_us', '32', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Work At IdeaBase\",\"slug\":\"jobs\",\"postDate\":1453825080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"525\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Qualifications<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our student employees come from a variety of backgrounds and benefit from our comprehensive service offering. Our student employees are:<\\/p><ul><li>Part-time or full-time Kent State University students<\\/li><li>Taking at least 6 credit hours<\\/li><li>Who are passionate about design<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\"}},\"554\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"531\"]}},\"555\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Degree Programs<\\/h2><p>Our students are primarily from the College of Communication and Information, but we have team members from other majors as well. &nbsp;Some of our past student majors include:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Visual Communication<\\/li><li>Design<\\/li><li>Communication Studies<\\/li><li>Advertising<\\/li><li>Public Relations<\\/li><li>Journalism<\\/li><li>Computer Information Systems<\\/li><li>Computer Science<\\/li><li>User Experience Design<\\/li><li>Library & Information Science<\\/li><li>Digital Sciences<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n