 ('602', '515', '14', '150', 'en_us', '29', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"User Experience Testing Lab\",\"slug\":\"ux\",\"postDate\":1453822920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"517\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Eye Tracking Usability<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer both traditional desktop eye tracking as well as wearable eyetracking technologies from Tobii. Eye tracking allows our user experience designers to closely study your product to see exactly where users are (and aren\\u2019t) looking. Using this measurable data, we\\u2019re able to suggest user experience improvements that help your users complete their goals faster and easier. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our eye tracking software can produce stunning visualizations, including heat maps and gaze plots, to help you communicate your findings to your stakeholders. It\\u2019s also a great tool for academic research. In fact, IdeaBase was featured in a national study on multimedia journalism by the Reynolds Journalism Institute.<\\/p><h3>Introducing Tobii Glasses 2<\\/h3><p>For the first time, we\\u2019re able to accurately conduct testing on mobile devices, including phones and tablets, and environmental designs, such as store displays and product packaging using the state of the art Tobii Glasses 2.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\"}},\"553\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h3><\\/h3>\"}},\"552\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"564\"]}},\"518\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>In-Person and Remote Usability Testing<\\/h2><p>We offer task-based usability studies that are conducted in-person by our research team. &nbsp;We\\u2019re also able to conduct remote user research using a variety of online tools. &nbsp;Our team can assist with recruiting, writing testing scripts and analyzing testing results.<\\/p>\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"599\"]}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Open Device Testing Lab<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With a variety of mobile devices on the market, it\\u2019s critical that your website or app translates across platforms and offers a consistent user experience. That\\u2019s where our Open Device Lab comes in. &nbsp;With onsite access to over 20 of the most popular devices (and expanding), our lab is a great place to test for bugs and implement fixes.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Partnering with Open Device Lab, any clients can now schedule a time to use our device lab at no charge!<\\/p><p>We currently offer access to the following devices:<\\/p><ul><li>Apple iPhone 4<\\/li><li>Apple iPhone 5<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy S4<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy Tab<\\/li><li>Apple iPad 2<\\/li><li>Toshiba Windows Laptop<\\/li><\\/ul><p>If you\'d like to come in and use the lab, just contact us by email, phone or via the form below. &nbsp;Have an old device that you\\u2019re no longer using? Donate it to our non-profit agency using this form.<\\/p>\"}},\"537\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Donate a Device\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/opendevicelab.com\\/DYDD\"}}},\"148\":\"Our on-site UX Testing Lab offers clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. We offer usability testing, Tobii eyetracking, and testing across a variety of mobile devices to ensure cross-platform functionality.\",\"37\":[\"449\"],\"135\":\"<p>We proudly manage our own in-house User Experience Testing Lab. This on-site lab complements our design services by offering clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. The lab is operated by an experienced User Experience Designer and a team of graduate students from Kent State\\u2019s renowned User Experience Design master\\u2019s program.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-04 17:23:45', '2016-02-04 17:23:45', '6cba4d80-5df7-431a-aebc-4acd158fc34a'),
 ('603', '492', '14', '150', 'en_us', '25', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"About IdeaBase\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1453394220,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"594\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>DELIVERING MEANINGFUL DESIGN SOLUTIONS<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Thanks to the diverse talent of our student employees, we offer a comprehensive service offering that includes advertising, branding, copywriting, identity design, marketing research, web design, usability studies, environmental design services and&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/dev\\/prototype\\/templates\\/process.php\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/services#entry:109:url\\\">much more<\\/a>. As part of a thriving university community, we also have access to additional resources to enhance our suite of services.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"533\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoURL\":\"<iframe width=\\\"560\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/VqQZbh8P8AI\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen><\\/iframe>\",\"videoCaption\":\" In this IdeaBase student-produced video, our students talk about their experiences working at IdeaBase.\"}},\"534\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>IN THE HEART OF DOWNTOWN KENT<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our office space&mdash;conveniently located in Downtown Kent&mdash;features an open layout with a conference room, creative workspace, educational area and <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/prod\\/ux#entry:515:url\\\">UX Testing Lab<\\/a>; it\\u2019s a great space for collaboration for students and clients alike!<\\/p>\"}},\"535\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Visit us today!\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":[\"557\"]}},\"551\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"538\"]}},\"536\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>A LEGACY OF STUDENT-LED DESIGN SOLUTIONS<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Formerly the Tannery, IdeaBase opened in 2009 as the brainchild of Jim Gaudino, the founding dean of the <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/cci\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">College of Communication and Information (CCI)<\\/a>. Gaudino worked with the directors from each of the CCI schools to develop a vision for a student-staffed organization where students could receive hands-on experience. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In 2014, to better reflect its core mission of providing unique educational experiences while delivering quality design solutions, the Tannery transformed into IdeaBase. Within the same year, IdeaBase expanded its service offering with the addition of <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/glyphix\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Glyphix<\\/a>, a classroom studio experience from the <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/vcd\\\">School of Visual Communication Design<\\/a>. IdeaBase continues to operate as part of the CCI, always evolving to bring new services and experiences to the university community and beyond.<\\/p>\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Learn More About Our Team\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":[\"108\"]}}},\"148\":\"Located in Downtown Kent, OH, IdeaBase is a student-powered design agency that bridges the gap between classroom and career. IdeaBase brings together top-performing Kent State students with unique backgrounds to tackle real-world client problems. \",\"37\":[\"601\"],\"135\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we bridge the gap between classroom and career by bringing together top-performing Kent State students to tackle real-world client problems. Our team represents a variety of backgrounds, including Visual Communication Design, Public Relations, Advertising, Computer Information Systems, Digital Sciences, Marketing and Communication Studies students.<br><\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-04 17:24:55', '2016-02-04 17:24:55', 'f2ccbae9-19c8-4b64-a6fa-5b337c469fee'),
 ('604', '365', '4', '150', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Florence Tour Campaign\",\"slug\":\"florence-tour-kent-state-college-of-communication-and-information\",\"postDate\":1451581860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"373\"],\"61\":[\"149\"],\"9\":\"<p>The Florence Alumni & Friends Tour campaign was developed for Kent State\'s College of Communication and Information with the goal of promoting an exclusive trip to Florence, Italy for alumni of the college. IdeaBase designers created a custom design system that was used across many different printed and digital pieces.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The campaign included:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>A printed book, explaining the benefits of attending the trip<\\/li><li>A folded invitation, mailed to CCI alumni<\\/li><li>A website, to which those interested were directed for more information<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Florence Tour campaign won a Solver ADDY&nbsp;from the Akron Advertising Federation in February 2015 as part&nbsp;of the professional Campaign category.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"364\"],\"88\":[\"177\",\"178\",\"179\"],\"104\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-04 19:42:17', '2016-02-04 19:42:17', 'aa5e25c9-e827-4e3c-83e6-bc5ce91afc93'),
