 ('652', '403', '4', '573', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"IdeaBase: Powered by Kent State Students\",\"slug\":\"ideabase-powered-by-kent-state-students\",\"postDate\":1452027540,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"402\"],\"61\":[\"320\",\"326\",\"146\"],\"9\":\"<p>Students and staff at IdeaBase speak about their experiences working on real-world client projects. Directed, edited and filmed exclusively by students at IdeaBase, the video shows how students from various backgrounds put into action what they\\u2019ve learned in their Kent State University classes. IdeaBase is a student-run creative agency in downtown Kent and is a service of the College of Communication and Information.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"642\"],\"88\":[\"180\"],\"104\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI\"}}', '2016-02-04 23:25:55', '2016-02-04 23:25:55', '805b78b2-0c57-4b29-a0d1-deea95eb90ee'),
 ('653', '357', '4', '573', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"State Library of Ohio Website\",\"slug\":\"state-library-of-ohio\",\"postDate\":1451580840,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"396\"],\"61\":[\"120\",\"316\",\"323\",\"67\",\"423\",\"146\"],\"9\":\"<p>IdeaBase redesigned the State Library of Ohio website in May 2015. &nbsp;The site&nbsp;features a new interface, improved site navigation, and enhanced search functionality. &nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=LeQZE5-ar3Q\\\">View the video<\\/a>&nbsp;to see the site in action, or<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/library.ohio.gov\\/\\\">&nbsp;visit the site<\\/a>&nbsp;to learn more.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"643\",\"602\"],\"88\":[\"175\"],\"104\":\"https:\\/\\/library.ohio.gov\\/\"}}', '2016-02-04 23:27:44', '2016-02-04 23:27:44', 'a6da9eed-703e-4488-bfad-d3a18fe2e0d2'),
 ('654', '365', '4', '573', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Florence Tour Campaign\",\"slug\":\"florence-tour-kent-state-college-of-communication-and-information\",\"postDate\":1451581860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"373\"],\"61\":[\"149\"],\"9\":\"<p>The Florence Alumni & Friends Tour campaign was developed for Kent State\'s College of Communication and Information with the goal of promoting an exclusive trip to Florence, Italy for alumni of the college. IdeaBase designers created a custom design system that was used across many different printed and digital pieces.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The campaign included:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>A printed book, explaining the benefits of attending the trip<\\/li><li>A folded invitation, mailed to CCI alumni<\\/li><li>A website, to which those interested were directed for more information<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Florence Tour campaign won a Solver ADDY&nbsp;from the Akron Advertising Federation in February 2015 as part&nbsp;of the professional Campaign category.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"647\",\"650\",\"644\",\"645\",\"649\"],\"88\":[\"177\",\"178\",\"179\"],\"104\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-04 23:32:22', '2016-02-04 23:32:22', 'bdf6e373-213c-4aa4-bff0-5073b929e129'),
 ('655', '353', '4', '573', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"ICE Consulting Branding \\/ Website\",\"slug\":\"ice-consulting\",\"postDate\":1451580420,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"399\"],\"61\":[\"320\",\"316\",\"120\",\"119\",\"146\"],\"9\":\"<p>IdeaBase redesigned the Ice Consulting&nbsp;website and Glyphix (kentglyphix.org) created a new brand identity and logo for Ice Consulting&nbsp;in July&nbsp;2015. The website uses a customized template from Squarespace.com, with colors, type and custom-designed iconography that matches the new ICE identity and the content was written and positioned to match the ICE business goals and increase search optimization. The website was also designed to be responsive and scale across multiple devices.<br><\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"651\"],\"88\":[\"177\",\"178\",\"175\"],\"104\":\"http:\\/\\/iceconsulting.org\\/\"}}', '2016-02-04 23:33:25', '2016-02-04 23:33:25', '7b567b3b-0aa7-4e3a-85c1-e68f378f28f9'),
