 ('671', '148', '15', '150', 'en_us', '23', '', '{\"typeId\":\"15\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Work\",\"slug\":\"projects-homepage\",\"postDate\":1453923363,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"590\"],\"71\":\"How we\'re making a difference\",\"72\":\"<p>We make a positive impact on your design and our student designers by taking the time to build right. Read case studies from our past projects to see for yourself.<\\/p>\",\"109\":\"IdeaBase Classroom Experiences\",\"74\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we want our student employees to succeed. That\\u2019s why we partner with Glyphix to teach the next generation through studio experiences. Our students develop and exercise project-based skills in marketing, design, research and more. Additionally, our Responsive Web Design class ensures the next generation of designers and developers understand how to create highly functional and usable websites.<\\/p>\",\"73\":\"Helping our students succeed\",\"148\":\"We\'re not just transforming our clients\' products and brands with our award-winning design solutions; we\'re transforming our student employees by giving them the chance to work directly with clients, managing all stages of design production.\",\"37\":[\"281\"],\"110\":\"See all projects\",\"69\":\"Our Past Work Speaks for Itself\",\"70\":\"<p>We deliver awarding-winning, quality design solutions that transform our clients\\u2019 products and brands. In turn, our talented students get the chance to work directly with clients, developing proposals, managing projects and handling all stages of design production.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-05 22:19:17', '2016-02-05 22:19:17', '48b92985-7ff0-4d24-951b-b5feef301067'),
 ('672', '109', '12', '150', 'en_us', '28', '', '{\"typeId\":\"12\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Services\",\"slug\":\"process-index\",\"postDate\":1453923350,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"591\"],\"148\":\"Let our suite of user research, design and testing services guide your product development; we offer everything from competitive analysis to graphic and Web design to eyetracking and usability testing in our very own UX Testing Lab.\",\"37\":[\"281\"],\"106\":\"<p>While our unique business model allows us to deliver high-quality products at an affordable cost, there\\u2019s no \\u201cone size fits all\\u201d when it comes to individual client needs. We work with our clients upfront to define goals and timelines to ensure that we deliver a great end-product within the project\\u2019s constraints. Together, we\\u2019ll plan and build something great, and it won\\u2019t break the bank.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Contact us today for a quote.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"107\":\"Sounds great, how much does it cost?\",\"79\":\"<p>We support our clients\\u2019 design initiatives from the early discovery phase through implementation (or anywhere in between). Whether you\\u2019re laying the foundation for your product\\u2019s success, or building out and refining your design, we\\u2019re here to help. And we do all of this right here locally from our fabulous office space in downtown Kent.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"42\":\"Our design services are tailored to you\",\"94\":{\"183\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Discover\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Discover who your users are and what they are looking for in your product.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"User Interviews\"},{\"col1\":\"Surveys\"},{\"col1\":\"Competitive Analysis\"},{\"col1\":\"Persona Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Focus Groups\"},{\"col1\":\"Heuristics \"}],\"icon1\":[\"252\"],\"icon2\":[\"253\"],\"icon3\":[\"248\"],\"icon4\":[\"257\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"245\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our targeted user research methods empower you to more effectively address your users\'&nbsp;needs.<\\/p>\"}},\"184\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Design\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Design a creative product that delivers on user and business needs.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"Print & Graphic Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Video Production\"},{\"col1\":\"Email Marketing\"},{\"col1\":\"Web Design & Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Content Strategy\"},{\"col1\":\"Environmental Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Brand Identity \"},{\"col1\":\"Social Media Campaigns\"}],\"icon1\":[\"249\"],\"icon2\":[\"254\"],\"icon3\":[\"256\"],\"icon4\":[\"246\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"244\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our design strategies, whether through print, video or web, deliver custom solutions that&nbsp;promote both business and customer needs.<\\/p>\"}},\"185\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Refine\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Refine an existing product with our advanced testing process.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"In-Person Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Remote Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Device & Performance Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Eyetracking Usability \"}],\"icon1\":[\"247\"],\"icon2\":[\"250\"],\"icon3\":[\"251\"],\"icon4\":[\"255\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"258\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our advanced usability testing tools, including eye tracking, allow you to evaluate the effectiveness of design solutions.<\\/p>\"}}},\"108\":\"More about our UX Testing Lab\",\"80\":\"<p>We can test the performance and usability of your product on various devices in our User Experience Testing Lab. This is a great resource to ensure that your product translates across all platforms.\\r\\n<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-05 22:19:59', '2016-02-05 22:19:59', '9b104a70-6dce-421a-8b4d-f2a3680c797a'),
 ('673', '108', '11', '150', 'en_us', '25', '', '{\"typeId\":\"11\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"People\",\"slug\":\"staff-profile-index\",\"postDate\":1445610228,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"592\"],\"39\":\"<p>We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s design, advertising, user experience, computer science and&nbsp;electronic media programs. Our students work under the guidance of full-time staff members from the College of Communication of Information and a <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ideabase.jmc.kent.edu\\/prod\\/people\\/board#entry:539:url\\\">professional\\/faculty&nbsp;advisory board<\\/a>, ensuring we produce the highest quality products for our clients and <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ideabase.jmc.kent.edu\\/prod\\/people\\/alumni#entry:540:url\\\">numerous alumni<\\/a> who are poised for real-world success.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s design, advertising, user experience, computer science and electronic media programs. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.\",\"37\":[\"281\"],\"38\":\"Our People are Passionate about Design\",\"45\":\"\",\"41\":\"We empower our student employees to imagine, create and deliver quality designs while gaining real-world experience on client-facing projects. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.\",\"58\":\"Work for IdeaBase\",\"40\":\"Work for IdeaBase\"}}', '2016-02-05 22:20:23', '2016-02-05 22:20:23', 'ad818e87-66fb-4137-80ee-d4fc5da9f554'),
