 ('677', '314', '4', '150', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Kent State Athletics Annual Report 2015\",\"slug\":\"kent-state-athletics-annual-report-2015\",\"postDate\":1441771200,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"395\"],\"61\":[\"120\",\"320\",\"236\",\"315\",\"323\",\"146\"],\"9\":\"<p>IdeaBase was brought on board for the second year in a row to develop and design Kent State University Athletics\' year-in-review\\/annual report.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The interactive report is designed in HTML\\/CSS&nbsp;and this year features a single-page design&nbsp;(with supplemental article pages). The design is composed to photos, text and custom icons that match the university\'s blue and gold branding.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We went through a process of discovert, content gathering, design\\/architerture and development over a period of 5 months.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>From a technical perspective, the site utilizes:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Jekyll, a static site generator that doesn\'t require a full content management system<\\/li><li>Grunt, for task running, including image resizing, browser refreshing and code compiling<\\/li><li>SASS&nbsp;for writing CSS&nbsp;for efficiency<\\/li><li>CSS&nbsp;animations<\\/li><li>Image and JavaScript compression and lazy loading for optimal performance<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The site launched in September 2015.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"311\"],\"161\":\"1\",\"88\":[\"175\"],\"104\":\"http:\\/\\/www.supportgoldenflashes.com\\/2015_Annual_Report\\/\"}}', '2016-02-05 22:44:58', '2016-02-05 22:44:58', 'ccdc31e0-9b5e-4ea9-9c0f-593607c74eb2'),
 ('678', '403', '4', '150', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"IdeaBase: Powered by Kent State Students Video\",\"slug\":\"ideabase-powered-by-kent-state-students\",\"postDate\":1452027540,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"402\"],\"61\":[\"320\",\"326\",\"146\"],\"9\":\"<p>Students and staff at IdeaBase speak about their experiences working on real-world client projects. Directed, edited and filmed exclusively by students at IdeaBase, the video shows how students from various backgrounds put into action what they\\u2019ve learned in their Kent State University classes. IdeaBase is a student-run creative agency in downtown Kent and is a service of the College of Communication and Information.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"642\"],\"161\":\"1\",\"88\":[\"180\"],\"104\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI\",\"162\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI\"}}', '2016-02-06 05:52:22', '2016-02-06 05:52:22', 'af2775c5-da56-4854-9f09-1052915b4ac2'),
 ('679', '492', '14', '150', 'en_us', '26', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"About IdeaBase\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1453394220,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"594\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>DELIVERING MEANINGFUL DESIGN SOLUTIONS<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Thanks to the diverse talent of our student employees, we offer a comprehensive service offering that includes advertising, branding, copywriting, identity design, marketing research, web design, usability studies, environmental design services and&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/new\\/dev\\/prototype\\/templates\\/process.php\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ideabase.jmc.kent.edu\\/prod\\/services#entry:109:url\\\">much more<\\/a>. As part of a thriving university community, we also have access to additional resources to enhance our suite of services.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"533\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoURL\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI\",\"videoCaption\":\" In this IdeaBase student-produced video, our students talk about their experiences working at IdeaBase.\"}},\"534\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>IN THE HEART OF DOWNTOWN KENT<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our office space&mdash;conveniently located in Downtown Kent&mdash;features an open layout with a conference room, creative workspace, educational area and <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ideabase.jmc.kent.edu\\/prod\\/ux#entry:515:url\\\">UX Testing Lab<\\/a>; it\\u2019s a great space for collaboration for students and clients alike!<\\/p>\"}},\"535\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Visit us today!\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":[\"557\"]}},\"551\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"538\"]}},\"536\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>A LEGACY OF STUDENT-LED DESIGN SOLUTIONS<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Formerly the Tannery, IdeaBase opened in 2009 as the brainchild of Jim Gaudino, the founding dean of the <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/cci\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">College of Communication and Information (CCI)<\\/a>. Gaudino worked with the directors from each of the CCI schools to develop a vision for a student-staffed organization where students could receive hands-on experience. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In 2014, to better reflect its core mission of providing unique educational experiences while delivering quality design solutions, the Tannery transformed into IdeaBase. Within the same year, IdeaBase expanded its service offering with the addition of <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/glyphix\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Glyphix<\\/a>, a classroom studio experience from the <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/vcd\\\">School of Visual Communication Design<\\/a>. IdeaBase continues to operate as part of the CCI, always evolving to bring new services and experiences to the university community and beyond.<\\/p>\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"buttonInternalLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonNameInternal\":\"Learn More About Our Team\",\"buttonLinkInternal\":[\"108\"]}}},\"148\":\"Located in Downtown Kent, OH, IdeaBase is a student-powered design agency that bridges the gap between classroom and career. IdeaBase brings together top-performing Kent State students with unique backgrounds to tackle real-world client problems. \",\"37\":[\"601\"],\"135\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we bridge the gap between classroom and career by bringing together top-performing Kent State students to tackle real-world client problems. Our team represents a variety of backgrounds, including Visual Communication Design, Public Relations, Advertising, Computer Information Systems, Digital Sciences, Marketing and Communication Studies students.<br><\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-06 05:54:03', '2016-02-06 05:54:03', '024017d6-d883-46aa-9da8-46a17fa07697'),
