 ('694', '422', '4', '150', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Kent State Online Orientation Video\",\"slug\":\"orientation-video\",\"postDate\":1452028860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"685\"],\"61\":[\"326\",\"315\"],\"9\":\"<p>The Student Orientation video for the Office of Continuing and Distance Education was produced throughout Summer 2015. &nbsp;Our videographers worked with the client to&nbsp;capture&nbsp;the essence of Kent State University and downtown Kent. The video is now shown to Kent State&nbsp;online students to give them a sense of belonging.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"631\"],\"161\":\"1\",\"88\":[\"180\"],\"104\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=v2DbiTSfvsQ\",\"162\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=v2DbiTSfvsQ\"}}', '2016-02-06 06:38:03', '2016-02-06 06:38:03', '7928d0fb-a270-4fe1-addf-b8a56d870342'),
 ('695', '108', '11', '150', 'en_us', '26', '', '{\"typeId\":\"11\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"People\",\"slug\":\"staff-profile-index\",\"postDate\":1445610228,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"592\"],\"39\":\"<p>We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s communication&nbsp;programs. Our students work under the guidance of full-time staff members from the <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/cci\\\">College of Communication of Information<\\/a> and a <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ideabase.jmc.kent.edu\\/prod\\/people\\/board#entry:539:url\\\">professional \\/&nbsp;faculty&nbsp;advisory board<\\/a>, ensuring we produce the highest quality products for our clients. &nbsp;Our commitment to real-world experience ensures our&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ideabase.jmc.kent.edu\\/prod\\/people\\/alumni#entry:540:url\\\">numerous alumni<\\/a>&nbsp;are poised for real-world success upon graduation.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s design, advertising, user experience, computer science and electronic media programs. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.\",\"37\":[\"281\"],\"38\":\"Our People are Passionate about Design\",\"45\":\"\",\"41\":\"We empower our student employees to imagine, create and deliver quality designs while gaining real-world experience on client-facing projects. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.\",\"58\":\"Work for IdeaBase\",\"40\":\"Work for IdeaBase\"}}', '2016-02-06 06:52:21', '2016-02-06 06:52:21', '65cd8473-9920-4a2a-a4c4-b05dfe04ecaa'),
 ('696', '108', '11', '150', 'en_us', '27', '', '{\"typeId\":\"11\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"People\",\"slug\":\"staff-profile-index\",\"postDate\":1445610228,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"592\"],\"39\":\"<p>We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s communication&nbsp;programs. Our students work under the guidance of full-time staff members from the <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/cci\\\">College of Communication of Information<\\/a> and a <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ideabase.jmc.kent.edu\\/prod\\/people\\/board#entry:539:url\\\">professional \\/&nbsp;faculty&nbsp;advisory board<\\/a>, ensuring we produce the highest quality products for our clients. &nbsp;Our commitment to real-world experience ensures our&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ideabase.jmc.kent.edu\\/prod\\/people\\/alumni#entry:540:url\\\">numerous alumni<\\/a>&nbsp;are poised for real-world success upon graduation.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"We hire only the best students from Kent State\'s design, advertising, user experience, computer science and electronic media programs. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.\",\"37\":[\"281\"],\"38\":\"Our People are Passionate about Design\",\"45\":\"\",\"41\":\"We empower our student employees to imagine, create and deliver quality designs while gaining real-world experience on client-facing projects. Our student employees get to put their design skills to the test, build their resumes and jumpstart their careers.\",\"58\":\"Work for IdeaBase\",\"40\":\"Work for IdeaBase\"}}', '2016-02-06 06:52:47', '2016-02-06 06:52:47', 'b8b74401-9f71-4802-9ca9-b79d5e7e1694'),
 ('697', '515', '14', '150', 'en_us', '30', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"User Experience Testing Lab\",\"slug\":\"ux\",\"postDate\":1453822920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"517\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Eye Tracking Usability<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer both traditional desktop eye tracking as well as wearable eyetracking technologies from Tobii. Eye tracking allows our user experience designers to closely study your product to see exactly where users are (and aren\\u2019t) looking. Using this measurable data, we\\u2019re able to suggest user experience improvements that help your users complete their goals faster and easier. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our eye tracking software can produce stunning visualizations, including heat maps and gaze plots, to help you communicate your findings to your stakeholders. It\\u2019s also a great tool for academic research. In fact, IdeaBase was featured in a national study on multimedia journalism by the Reynolds Journalism Institute.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Introducing Tobii Glasses 2<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>For the first time, we\\u2019re able to accurately conduct testing on mobile devices, including phones and tablets, and environmental designs, such as store displays and product packaging using the state of the art Tobii Glasses 2.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\"}},\"553\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"\"}},\"552\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"564\"]}},\"518\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>In-Person and Remote Usability Testing<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer task-based usability studies that are conducted in-person by our research team. &nbsp;We\\u2019re also able to conduct remote user research using a variety of online tools. &nbsp;Our team can assist with recruiting, writing testing scripts and analyzing testing results.<\\/p>\"}},\"600\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"599\"]}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Open Device Testing Lab<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With a variety of mobile devices on the market, it\\u2019s critical that your website or app translates across platforms and offers a consistent user experience. That\\u2019s where our Open Device Lab comes in. &nbsp;With onsite access to over 20 of the most popular devices (and expanding), our lab is a great place to test for bugs and implement fixes.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Partnering with Open Device Lab, any clients can now schedule a time to use our device lab at no charge!<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We currently offer access to the following devices:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Apple iPhone 4<\\/li><li>Apple iPhone 5<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy S4<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy Tab<\\/li><li>Apple iPad 2<\\/li><li>Toshiba Windows Laptop<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you\'d like to come in and use the lab, just contact us by email, phone or via the form below. &nbsp;Have an old device that you\\u2019re no longer using? Donate it to our non-profit agency using this form.<\\/p>\"}},\"537\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Donate a Device\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/opendevicelab.com\\/DYDD\"}}},\"148\":\"Our on-site UX Testing Lab offers clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. We offer usability testing, Tobii eyetracking, and testing across a variety of mobile devices to ensure cross-platform functionality.\",\"37\":[\"590\"],\"135\":\"<p>We proudly manage our own in-house User Experience Testing Lab. This on-site lab complements our design services by offering clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. The lab is operated by an experienced User Experience Designer and a team of graduate students from Kent State\\u2019s renowned User Experience Design master\\u2019s program.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-06 06:54:46', '2016-02-06 06:54:46', '36d127b7-4c56-4e89-a416-8a2cdf2a845a'),
 ('698', '524', '14', '150', 'en_us', '37', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Work At IdeaBase\",\"slug\":\"jobs\",\"postDate\":1453825080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"525\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Qualifications<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our student employees come from a variety of backgrounds and benefit from our comprehensive service offering. Our student employees are:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Part-time or full-time Kent State University students<\\/li><li>Taking at least 6 credit hours<\\/li><li>Who are passionate about design<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"554\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"531\"]}},\"555\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Degree Programs<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our students are primarily from the College of Communication and Information, but we have team members from other majors as well. &nbsp;Some of our past student majors include:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Visual Communication<\\/li><li>Design<\\/li><li>Communication Studies<\\/li><li>Advertising<\\/li><li>Public Relations<\\/li><li>Journalism<\\/li><li>Computer Information Systems<\\/li><li>Computer Science<\\/li><li>User Experience Design<\\/li><li>Library & Information Science<\\/li><li>Digital Sciences<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoURL\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI\",\"videoCaption\":\"Students Explain What It\'s Like to Work at IdeaBase\"}},\"597\":{\"type\":\"callOut\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"callOut\":\"Apply for a Job\",\"callOutText\":\"<p>Think you\\u2019ll be a great fit? &nbsp;Email your resume to&nbsp;<a href=\\\"mailto:info@ideabasekent.com\\\">info@ideabasekent.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Not a stude