 ('719', '317', '3', '456', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Christopher Uhler\",\"slug\":\"christopher-uhler\",\"postDate\":1451403900,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Christopher&nbsp;is a Graduate Student studying User Experience Design and will graduate in August, 2016.&nbsp;&nbsp;He also has a B.A. in Film Studies from&nbsp;Ohio State University.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Beyond IdeaBase, Chris also works as a Production Manager at Bent Tree Coffee Roasters. In his spare time&nbsp;Chris enjoys spending time with his family, backpacking&nbsp;and photography.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\",\"77\":\"M.S. User Experience Design\",\"4\":\"cuhler@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Christopher\",\"7\":\"\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"User Experience Designer\",\"114\":\"Uhler\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"290\"],\"89\":{\"488\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Christopher\'s photography site\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.chrisuhler.com\"}},\"572\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Linkedin\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/christopher-uhler-67023615\"}}}}}', '2016-02-08 03:10:37', '2016-02-08 03:10:37', '8b7e49d9-28c6-4b66-914e-bfaf0976a1bf'),
 ('720', '318', '3', '456', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Courtney Kaminski\",\"slug\":\"courtney-kaminski\",\"postDate\":1451404020,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>My name is Courtney Kaminski. I am a senior advertising student at Kent State, graduating in May 2016.&nbsp;I am an account manager at IdeaBase, and I also have a digital marketing internship and I work at FedEx Office in Kent. I have also had a copywriting internship, so I have plenty of writing experience!&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>I have eight guinea pigs and two cats, all of which are very spoiled. I spend a lot of time reading and learning about design. I love to cook and can usually be found searching the Web for new recipes.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Advertising \",\"4\":\"ckaminski@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Courtney\",\"7\":\"\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Account Manager\",\"114\":\"Kaminski\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"292\"],\"89\":{\"485\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Courtney\'s Portfolio\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.courtneykaminski.com\\/\"}}}}}', '2016-02-08 03:11:48', '2016-02-08 03:11:48', 'f306f796-df5c-4979-952c-07716ed87b67'),
 ('721', '320', '3', '456', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"John Vrhovnik\",\"slug\":\"john-vrhovnik\",\"postDate\":1451404440,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>John Vrhovnik is a Bachelor of Fine Arts in Visual Communication Design major and Digital Sciences minor, graduating in spring of 2016. He works as a Graphic Designer at IdeaBase. John enjoys making hand-drawn lettering, working out, cooking, hiking\\/kayaking&nbsp;and making friends<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Visual Communication Design\",\"4\":\"jvrhovnik@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"John\",\"7\":\"I can draw nice letters, but my actual handwriting is worse than a first graders.\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Designer\",\"114\":\"Vrhovnik\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"294\"],\"89\":{\"584\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Website\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/cargocollective.com\\/johnvrhovnik\"}},\"586\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"LinkedIn\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/johnvrhovnik\"}},\"585\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Instagram\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/digupthedead\\/\"}},\"583\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Dribbble\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/dribbble.com\\/JohnVrhovnik\"}}}}}', '2016-02-08 03:13:45', '2016-02-08 03:13:45', '5430aa82-1316-4b4d-b1ea-544ae6643ffa'),
 ('722', '322', '3', '456', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Mario Fasolo\",\"slug\":\"mario-fasolo\",\"postDate\":1451405100,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Mario is a determined graphic designer eager to&nbsp;begin his professional career after he graduates in&nbsp;May of 2016.&nbsp;He has been in Photoshop since the young age of 10, which made it a perfect fit when the Athletics Department needed an IdeaBase employee to take over their work. Mario enjoys all things design, from brochures to mobile applications, and also has a passion for portraiture and concert photography...and creates abstract surreal art on his phone when he isn\'t too busy.&nbsp; Outside of working, Mario likes to attend rock concerts, create cappuccinos&nbsp;and pretend that he knows how to sing.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Visual Communication Design\",\"4\":\"mfasolo@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Mario\",\"7\":\"\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Designer\",\"114\":\"Fasolo\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"295\"],\"89\":{\"484\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Mario\'s Portfolio\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/mariofasolo.com\\/\"}}}}}', '2016-02-08 03:14:40', '2016-02-08 03:14:40', '437ce14e-3652-4116-8f70-30fe7f421f97'),
 ('723', '213', '3', '456', 'en_us', '10', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Rachel Kozy\",\"slug\":\"rachel-kozy\",\"postDate\":1450376520,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>My name is Rachel Kozy and I am a visual communication design student at Kent State University graduating in May 2016. Although I love all aspects of design, I am especially interested in visual branding, UI\\/UX and typography. In the past, I have interned with MTV in New York City and Go Media in Cleveland, and I am currently the president of my collegiate chapter of AIGA. When I\'m not designing, you\'ll likely find me playing video games or rewatching Avatar: The Last Airbender.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Visual Communication Design\",\"4\":\"rkozy@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Rachel\",\"7\":\"\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Designer\",\"114\":\"Kozy\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"299\"],\"89\":{\"458\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Rachel\'s Portfolio Site\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.rachelkozy.com\"}},\"459\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Linkedin\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/rachelkozy\"}},\"460\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Behance\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.behance.net\\/rachelkozy\"}}}}}', '2016-02-08 03:16:18', '2016-02-08 03:16:18', '17b95610-6783-44f4-9284-5aaad8806420'),
 ('724', '67', '3', '456', 'en_us', '26', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Reilly Hawkins \",\"slug\":\"reilly-hawkins\",\"postDate\":1442584980,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Reilly&nbsp;is an outfielder for the Kent State University baseball team. He enjoys being a \\u201ctechie\\u201d&nbsp;and loves Apple products and their&nbsp;innovations.&nbsp;Reilly is&nbsp;intrigued&nbsp;by&nbsp;how much technology is becoming a part of everyday society.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Computer Information Systems \",\"4\":\"rhawkins@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Reilly\",\"7\":\"I legally had my name changed in Kindergarten. It used to be Andrew Quaid Hawkins, however there were 4 other \\u201cAndrews\\u201d in my class so my mom wanted it to be more unique. Changed to Reilly William Hawkins.\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Web Programmer\",\"114\":\"Hawkins \",\"5\":\"440.221.9193\",\"27\":[\"300\"],\"89\":{\"437\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Twitter\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.twitter.com\\/reillyhawkins\"}},\"438\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"LinkedIn\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/profile\\/view?id=AAIAABtGIFwBrklv68_miVOWyVO8DJYNSDMRHX4&trk=nav_responsive_tab_profile_pic\"}}}}}', '2016-02-08 03:17:03', '2016-02-08 03:17:03', '9432bd7c-896f-44e3-a003-52f8f9bc6bc5'),
 ('725', '236', '3', '456', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Sarah Holzer\",\"slug\":\"sarah-holzer\",\"postDate\":1450378740,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>My name is Sarah and I love all things creative! Originally from Pittsburgh, I currently reside in Ohio while working towards my BFA degree in Visual Communication Design from Kent State University, where I\'m graduating&nbsp;in May of 2016.&nbsp;When I\'m not rattling my brain to creatively solve a problem, I love yoga, the outdoors, cooking (although sometimes the fire alarm is my kitchen timer), hanging out with my dog&nbsp;and Elvis.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Visual Communication Design\",\"4\":\"sholzer@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Sarah\",\"7\":\"\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Designer\",\"114\":\"Holzer\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"302\"],\"89\":{\"457\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Sarah\'s Portfolio \",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/sarahholzer.com\\/\"}}}}}', '2016-02-08 03:19:39', '2016-02-08 03:19:39', '965c7953-79e0-4d24-940a-891eacbf9d13'),
 ('726', '326', '3', '456', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Todd Thompson\",\"slug\":\"todd-thompson\",\"postDate\":1451405880,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Todd Thompson has an immense passion for anything involving cameras. Since Todd&nbsp;was 13 years old&nbsp;he could always be seen with a camera in his hands. Now pursuing a lifelong career in Video Journalism, starting at Kent State and IdeaBase, he hopes to work in the field&nbsp;and lend a hand in the current media transition from physical to digital format following his positions in Kent, Ohio.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Electronic Media Production\",\"4\":\"tthompson@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Todd\",\"7\":\" I play in two different bands and enjoy working in ceramics.\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Videographer\",\"114\":\"Thompson\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"305\"],\"89\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:20:47', '2016-02-08 03:20:47', 'a0549c57-9a1f-4885-9b89-7a2c21707653'),
 ('727', '147', '3', '456', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Victoria Ripepi\",\"slug\":\"victoria-ripepi\",\"postDate\":1446762360,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>My name is Victoria Ripepi and I am a 5th year senior graduating in May 2016 with a major in Communication Studies, concentration interpersonal. I\'m from Hudson, OH and came to Kent State because I am the oldest of 6 kids and didn\'t want to be far away from home. After being here for 5 years, I am very ready to move onto the next chapter of my life and begin finding a job out of Ohio. I am the event coordinator at IdeaBase and helped successfully plan over a 100 person Open House in the Fall of 2015. Now I will be joining IdeaBase this Spring 2016 as an Account Manager and I\'m very excited for that. I hope to get a job in corporate event planning and\\/or an experience marketing firm. Previous to working at IdeaBase, I worked for a small event planning company that put on 100 vendor art and craft shows throughout Northeast Ohio and the Columbus area. I am a people person and I always have a smile on my face. I have two&nbsp;cats, my favorite color is black and my favorite food is fried pickles.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Communication Studies and Interpersonal concentration\",\"4\":\"vripepi@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Victoria\",\"7\":\"\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Event Coordinator\",\"114\":\"Ripepi\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"307\"],\"89\":{\"507\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Linkedin\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/victoriaripepi\"}},\"508\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"\",\"staffSocLink\":\"\"}}}}}', '2016-02-08 03:22:36', '2016-02-08 03:22:36', 'e9c331b6-0916-41fa-98bd-7e0c124053eb'),
 ('728', '524', '14', '456', 'en_us', '42', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Work At IdeaBase\",\"slug\":\"jobs\",\"postDate\":1453825080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"525\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Qualifications<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our student employees come from a variety of backgrounds and benefit from our comprehensive service offering. Our student employees are:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Part-time or full-time Kent State University students<\\/li><li>Taking at least 6 credit hours<\\/li><li>Passionate about design<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"693\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoURL\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI\",\"videoCaption\":\"Students Explain What It\'s Like to Work at IdeaBase\"}},\"555\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Degree Programs<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our students are primarily from the College of Communication and Information, but we have team members from other majors as well. &nbsp;Some of our past student majors include:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Visual Communication<\\/li><li>Design<\\/li><li>Communication Studies<\\/li><li>Advertising<\\/li><li>Public Relations<\\/li><li>Journalism<\\/li><li>Computer Information Systems<\\/li><li>Computer Science<\\/li><li>User Experience Design<\\/li><li>Library & Information Science<\\/li><li>Digital Sciences<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"597\":{\"type\":\"callOut\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"callOut\":\"Apply for a Job\",\"callOutText\":\"<p>Think you\\u2019ll be a great fit? &nbsp;Email your resume to&nbsp;<a href=\\\"mailto:info@ideabasekent.com\\\">info@ideabasekent.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Not a student? Not a problem--you can still get involved by mentoring students, donating supplies or joining our professional advisory board. &nbsp;Contact&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/prod\\/people\\/kristin-dowling#entry:119:url\\\">Kristin Dowling<\\/a>, Business Development Manager, today.<\\/p>\",\"callOutImage\":[\"501\"]}}},\"148\":\"If you\'re a Kent State student who\'s passionate about design, we\'ve got a job for you. Our student employees--who are primarily from the College of Communication and Information--have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating. \",\"37\":[\"526\"],\"135\":\"<p>Put your design skills to the test. At IdeaBase, we believe that top-performing students should have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:24:34', '2016-02-08 03:24:34', '4e82cc79-a05f-432d-a7ee-f25e9a5ab666'),
 ('729', '524', '14', '456', 'en_us', '43', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Work At IdeaBase\",\"slug\":\"jobs\",\"postDate\":1453825080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"525\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Qualifications<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our student employees come from a variety of backgrounds and benefit from our comprehensive service offering. Our student employees are:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Part-time or full-time Kent State University students<\\/li><li>Taking at least 6 credit hours<\\/li><li>Passionate about design<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"693\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoURL\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI\",\"videoCaption\":\"Students Explain What It\'s Like to Work at IdeaBase\"}},\"555\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Degree Programs<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our students are primarily from the College of Communication and Information, but we have team members from other majors as well. &nbsp;Some of our past student majors include:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Visual Communication<\\/li><li>Design<\\/li><li>Communication Studies<\\/li><li>Advertising<\\/li><li>Public Relations<\\/li><li>Journalism<\\/li><li>Computer Information Systems<\\/li><li>Computer Science<\\/li><li>User Experience Design<\\/li><li>Library & Information Science<\\/li><li>Digital Sciences<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"597\":{\"type\":\"callOut\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"callOut\":\"Apply for a Job\",\"callOutText\":\"<p>Think you\\u2019ll be a great fit? &nbsp;Email your resume to&nbsp;<a href=\\\"mailto:info@ideabasekent.com\\\">info@ideabasekent.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Not a student? Not a problem--you can still get involved by mentoring students, donating supplies or joining our professional advisory board. &nbsp;Contact&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/prod\\/people\\/kristin-dowling#entry:119:url\\\">Kristin Dowling<\\/a>, Business Development Manager, today.<\\/p>\",\"callOutImage\":[\"501\"]}}},\"148\":\"If you\'re a Kent State student who\'s passionate about design, we\'ve got a job for you. Our student employees--who are primarily from the College of Communication and Information--have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating. \",\"37\":[\"526\"],\"135\":\"<p>Put your design skills to the test. At IdeaBase, we believe that top-performing students should have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:26:05', '2016-02-08 03:26:05', '471409a4-e11f-4531-a74a-4206e3e8c0a8'),
 ('730', '314', '4', '456', 'en_us', '10', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Kent State Athletics Annual Report 2015\",\"slug\":\"kent-state-athletics-annual-report-2015\",\"postDate\":1441771200,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"395\"],\"61\":[\"120\",\"320\",\"236\",\"315\",\"323\",\"146\"],\"9\":\"<p>IdeaBase was brought on board for the second year in a row to develop and design Kent State University Athletics\' year-in-review\\/annual report.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The interactive report is designed in HTML\\/CSS&nbsp;and this year features a single-page design&nbsp;(with supplemental article pages). The design is composed of&nbsp;photos, text and custom icons that match the university\'s blue and gold branding.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We went through a process of discovery, content gathering, design\\/architerture and development over a period of five&nbsp;months.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>From a technical perspective, the site utilizes:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Jekyll, a static site generator that doesn\'t require a full content management system<\\/li><li>Grunt&nbsp;for task running, including image resizing, browser refreshing and code compiling<\\/li><li>SASS&nbsp;for writing CSS&nbsp;for efficiency<\\/li><li>CSS&nbsp;animations<\\/li><li>Image and JavaScript compression and lazy loading for optimal performance<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The site launched in September 2015.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"311\"],\"161\":\"\",\"88\":[\"175\"],\"104\":\"http:\\/\\/www.supportgoldenflashes.com\\/2015_Annual_Report\\/\",\"162\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:38:36', '2016-02-08 03:38:36', 'd1d82ae3-6b58-4cec-8537-b923887679d6'),
 ('731', '420', '4', '456', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Schneller Environmental Design\",\"slug\":\"schneller-environmental-design\",\"postDate\":1452028800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"397\"],\"61\":\"\",\"9\":\"<p>The IdeaBase team for this project wanted to make huge impact because of Schneller\\u2019s status as the top&nbsp;designer for laminates and textile ooring for the transportation industry. For the conference room, the team&nbsp;of designers developed a map display that personifies&nbsp;Schneller\\u2019s global footprint. The team then designed a&nbsp;process gallery that illustrates the process of making&nbsp;laminates. Another dimension of this project included&nbsp;creating an image that displays a plane taking off from&nbsp;the runway. This piece is positioned directly outside&nbsp;Schneller\\u2019s conference room and provides a strong&nbsp;and powerful statement for their company.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":\"\",\"161\":\"\",\"88\":[\"433\"],\"104\":\"\",\"162\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:41:39', '2016-02-08 03:41:39', 'ef003544-3a87-41de-8ef4-0995dab9fcef'),
 ('732', '355', '4', '456', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"SLIS Website\",\"slug\":\"school-of-library-information-science\",\"postDate\":1451580660,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"400\"],\"61\":[\"120\",\"146\",\"423\",\"435\",\"442\"],\"9\":\"<p>IdeaBase took on the research, design and development for the School of Library & Information Science over a nine-month period, launching in January 2015.&nbsp;The website features a custom, responsive design template, research-backed content and navigation and was built in Drupal according to Kent State University\\u2019s Web standards.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"354\"],\"161\":\"\",\"88\":[\"177\",\"175\"],\"104\":\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/slis\",\"162\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:42:50', '2016-02-08 03:42:50', 'c286e4cc-b30e-4eff-a522-62ff6ce197fa'),
 ('733', '357', '4', '456', 'en_us', '10', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"State Library of Ohio Website\",\"slug\":\"state-library-of-ohio\",\"postDate\":1451580840,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"396\"],\"61\":[\"120\",\"316\",\"323\",\"67\",\"423\",\"146\"],\"9\":\"<p>IdeaBase redesigned the State Library of Ohio website in May 2015. &nbsp;The site&nbsp;features a new interface, improved site navigation&nbsp;and enhanced search functionality. &nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=LeQZE5-ar3Q\\\">View the video<\\/a>&nbsp;to see the site in action&nbsp;or<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/library.ohio.gov\\/\\\">&nbsp;visit the site<\\/a>&nbsp;to learn more.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"46\":[\"643\",\"602\"],\"161\":\"1\",\"88\":[\"175\"],\"104\":\"https:\\/\\/library.ohio.gov\\/\",\"162\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:43:30', '2016-02-08 03:43:30', '0e9d8687-4dae-4dfb-8228-bfcdd42d5c47'),
