 ('736', '524', '14', '456', 'en_us', '44', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Work At IdeaBase\",\"slug\":\"jobs\",\"postDate\":1453825080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"525\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Qualifications<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our student employees come from a variety of backgrounds and benefit from our comprehensive service offering. Our student employees are:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Part-time or full-time Kent State University students<\\/li><li>Taking at least 6 credit hours<\\/li><li>Passionate about design<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"693\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoURL\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI\",\"videoCaption\":\"Students Explain What It\'s Like to Work at IdeaBase\"}},\"555\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Degree Programs<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our students are primarily from the College of Communication and Information, but we have team members from other majors as well. &nbsp;Some of our past student majors include:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Visual Communication<\\/li><li>Design<\\/li><li>Communication Studies<\\/li><li>Advertising<\\/li><li>Public Relations<\\/li><li>Journalism<\\/li><li>Computer Information Systems<\\/li><li>Computer Science<\\/li><li>User Experience Design<\\/li><li>Library & Information Science<\\/li><li>Digital Sciences<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"597\":{\"type\":\"callOut\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"callOut\":\"Apply for a Job\",\"callOutText\":\"<p>Think you\\u2019ll be a great fit? &nbsp;Email your resume to&nbsp;<a href=\\\"mailto:info@ideabasekent.com\\\">info@ideabasekent.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Not a student? Not a problem&mdash;you can still get involved by mentoring students, donating supplies or joining our professional advisory board. &nbsp;Contact&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/prod\\/people\\/kristin-dowling#entry:119:url\\\">Kristin Dowling<\\/a>, Business Development Manager, today.<\\/p>\",\"callOutImage\":[\"501\"]}}},\"148\":\"If you\'re a Kent State student who\'s passionate about design, we\'ve got a job for you. Our student employees--who are primarily from the College of Communication and Information--have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating. \",\"37\":[\"526\"],\"135\":\"<p>Put your design skills to the test. At IdeaBase, we believe that top-performing students should have the opportunity to gain real-world experience before graduating.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:47:42', '2016-02-08 03:47:42', '000edcd1-19eb-490e-8c8e-f92d966eb397'),
 ('737', '515', '14', '456', 'en_us', '31', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"User Experience Testing Lab\",\"slug\":\"ux\",\"postDate\":1453822920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"517\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Eye Tracking Usability<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer both traditional desktop eye tracking as well as wearable eye&nbsp;tracking technologies from Tobii. Eye tracking allows our user experience designers to closely study your product to see exactly where users are (and aren\\u2019t) looking. Using this measurable data, we\\u2019re able to suggest user experience improvements that help your users complete their goals faster and easier. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our eye tracking software can produce stunning visualizations, including heat maps and gaze plots, to help you communicate your findings to your stakeholders. It\\u2019s also a great tool for academic research. In fact, IdeaBase was featured in a national study on multimedia journalism by the Reynolds Journalism Institute.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Introducing Tobii Glasses 2<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>For the first time, we\\u2019re able to accurately conduct testing on mobile devices, including phones and tablets, and environmental designs, such as store displays and product packaging using the state of the art Tobii Glasses 2.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\"}},\"553\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"\"}},\"552\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"564\"]}},\"518\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>In-Person and Remote Usability Testing<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer task-based usability studies that are conducted in-person by our research team. &nbsp;We\\u2019re also able to conduct remote user research using a variety of online tools. &nbsp;Our team can assist with recruiting, writing testing scripts and analyzing testing results.<\\/p>\"}},\"600\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"599\"]}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Open Device Testing Lab<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With a variety of mobile devices on the market, it\\u2019s critical that your website or app translates across platforms and offers a consistent user experience. That\\u2019s where our Open Device Lab comes in. &nbsp;With onsite access to over 20 of the most popular devices (and expanding), our lab is a great place to test for bugs and implement fixes.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Partnering with Open Device Lab, any clients can now schedule a time to use our device lab at no charge!<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We currently offer access to the following devices:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Apple iPhone 4<\\/li><li>Apple iPhone 5<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy S4<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy Tab<\\/li><li>Apple iPad 2<\\/li><li>Toshiba Windows Laptop<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you\'d like to come in and use the lab, just contact us by email, phone or via the form below. &nbsp;Have an old device that you\\u2019re no longer using? Donate it to our non-profit agency using this form.<\\/p>\"}},\"537\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Donate a Device\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/opendevicelab.com\\/DYDD\"}}},\"148\":\"Our on-site UX Testing Lab offers clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. We offer usability testing, Tobii eyetracking, and testing across a variety of mobile devices to ensure cross-platform functionality.\",\"37\":[\"590\"],\"135\":\"<p>We proudly manage our own in-house User Experience Testing Lab. This on-site lab complements our design services by offering clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. The lab is operated by an experienced User Experience Designer and a team of graduate students from Kent State\\u2019s renowned User Experience Design master\\u2019s program.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:51:28', '2016-02-08 03:51:28', '6130b974-82fa-4f7c-a631-6e07824212ca'),
 ('738', '515', '14', '456', 'en_us', '32', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"User Experience Testing Lab\",\"slug\":\"ux\",\"postDate\":1453822920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"517\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Eye Tracking Usability<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer both traditional desktop eye tracking as well as wearable eye&nbsp;tracking technologies from Tobii. Eye tracking allows our user experience designers to closely study your product to see exactly where users are (and aren\\u2019t) looking. Using this measurable data, we\\u2019re able to suggest user experience improvements that help your users complete their goals faster and easier. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our eye tracking software can produce stunning visualizations, including heat maps and gaze plots, to help you communicate your findings to your stakeholders. It\\u2019s also a great tool for academic research. In fact, IdeaBase was featured in a national study on multimedia journalism by the Reynolds Journalism Institute.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Introducing Tobii Glasses 2<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>For the first time, we\\u2019re able to accurately conduct testing on mobile devices, including phones and tablets, and environmental designs, such as store displays and product packaging using the state of the art Tobii Glasses 2.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\"}},\"553\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"\"}},\"552\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"564\"]}},\"518\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>In-Person and Remote Usability Testing<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer task-based usability studies that are conducted in-person by our research team. &nbsp;We\\u2019re also able to conduct remote user research using a variety of online tools. &nbsp;Our team can assist with recruiting, writing testing scripts and analyzing testing results.<\\/p>\"}},\"600\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"599\"]}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Open Device Testing Lab<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With a variety of mobile devices on the market, it\\u2019s critical that your website or app translates across platforms and offers a consistent user experience. That\\u2019s where our Open Device Lab comes in. &nbsp;With on-site access to over 20 of the most popular devices (and expanding), our lab is a great place to test for bugs and implement fixes.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Partnering with Open Device Lab, our&nbsp;clients can now schedule a time to use our device lab at no charge!<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We currently offer access to the following devices:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Apple iPhone 4<\\/li><li>Apple iPhone 5<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy S4<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy Tab<\\/li><li>Apple iPad 2<\\/li><li>Toshiba Windows Laptop<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you\'d like to come in and use the lab, just contact us by email, phone or via the form below. Have an old device that you\\u2019re no longer using? Donate it to our non-profit agency using this form.<\\/p>\"}},\"537\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Donate a Device\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/opendevicelab.com\\/DYDD\"}}},\"148\":\"Our on-site UX Testing Lab offers clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. We offer usability testing, Tobii eyetracking, and testing across a variety of mobile devices to ensure cross-platform functionality.\",\"37\":[\"590\"],\"135\":\"<p>We proudly manage our own in-house User Experience Testing Lab. This on-site lab complements our design services by offering clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. The lab is operated by an experienced User Experience Designer and a team of graduate students from Kent State\\u2019s renowned User Experience Design master\\u2019s program.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:54:12', '2016-02-08 03:54:12', '24e0ff6c-3ec8-4a0a-aeb3-70f9caa00cfc'),
 ('739', '109', '12', '456', 'en_us', '30', '', '{\"typeId\":\"12\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Services\",\"slug\":\"process-index\",\"postDate\":1453923350,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"591\"],\"148\":\"Let our suite of user research, design and testing services guide your product development; we offer everything from competitive analysis to graphic and Web design to eyetracking and usability testing in our very own UX Testing Lab.\",\"37\":[\"281\"],\"106\":\"<p>While our unique business model allows us to deliver high-quality products at an affordable cost, there\\u2019s no \\u201cone size fits all\\u201d when it comes to individual client needs. We work with our clients upfront to define goals and timelines to ensure that we deliver a great end&nbsp;product within the project\\u2019s constraints. Together, we\\u2019ll plan and build something great, and it won\\u2019t break the bank.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Contact us today for a quote.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"107\":\"Sounds great, how much does it cost?\",\"79\":\"<p>We support our clients\\u2019 design initiatives from the early discovery phase through implementation (or anywhere in between). Whether you\\u2019re laying the foundation for your product\\u2019s success, or building out and refining your design, we\\u2019re here to help. And we do all of this right here locally from our <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/prod\\/about#entry:492:url\\\">fabulous office space<\\/a> in downtown Kent.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"42\":\"Our design services are tailored to you\",\"94\":{\"183\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Discover\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Discover who your users are and what they are looking for in your product.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"User Interviews\"},{\"col1\":\"Surveys\"},{\"col1\":\"Competitive Analysis\"},{\"col1\":\"Persona Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Focus Groups\"},{\"col1\":\"Heuristics \"}],\"icon1\":[\"252\"],\"icon2\":[\"253\"],\"icon3\":[\"248\"],\"icon4\":[\"257\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"245\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our targeted user research methods empower you to more effectively address your users\'&nbsp;needs.<\\/p>\"}},\"184\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Design\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Design a creative product that delivers on user and business needs.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"Print & Graphic Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Video Production\"},{\"col1\":\"Email Marketing\"},{\"col1\":\"Web Design & Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Content Strategy\"},{\"col1\":\"Environmental Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Brand Identity \"},{\"col1\":\"Social Media Campaigns\"}],\"icon1\":[\"249\"],\"icon2\":[\"254\"],\"icon3\":[\"256\"],\"icon4\":[\"246\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"244\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our design strategies, whether through print, video or web, deliver custom solutions that&nbsp;promote both business and customer needs.<\\/p>\"}},\"185\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Refine\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Refine an existing product with our advanced testing process.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"In-Person Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Remote Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Device & Performance Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Eyetracking Usability \"}],\"icon1\":[\"247\"],\"icon2\":[\"250\"],\"icon3\":[\"251\"],\"icon4\":[\"255\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"258\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our advanced usability testing tools, including eye tracking, allow you to evaluate the effectiveness of design solutions.<\\/p>\"}}},\"108\":\"More about our UX Testing Lab\",\"80\":\"<p>We can test the performance and usability of your product on various devices in our User Experience Testing Lab. This is a great resource to ensure that your product translates across all platforms.\\r\\n<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-08 03:55:30', '2016-02-08 03:55:30', '2bcfd28d-e9b3-48ee-8924-912decbe1a84'),
 ('740', '120', '3', '150', 'en_us', '15', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Christopher Hallahan\",\"slug\":\"christopher-hallahan\",\"postDate\":1445536440,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Chris is a full-time user experience designer for<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ideabasekent.com\\/\\\"> <u>IdeaBase<\\/u><\\/a> and<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.kent.edu\\/cci\\\"> <u>Kent State University\\u2019s College of Communication and Information<\\/u><\\/a>. He manages research and interactive\\/web projects at IdeaBase, and works one-on-one with IdeaBase students to teach them web design, user experience and content strategy&nbsp;techniques. &nbsp;He also teaches a class on&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.rwdkent.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Responsive Web Design<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>His passions include responsive web design, usability, information architecture and content management system design.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"B.S. Electronic Media, M.A. User Experience Design\",\"4\":\"challahan@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Christopher\",\"26\":[\"5\"],\"3\":\"User Experience Designer\",\"114\":\"Hallahan\",\"5\":\"330-672-3031\",\"27\":[\"291\"],\"89\":{\"497\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Twitter\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.twitter.com\\/challahan\"}},\"610\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Website\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.chrishallahan.com\"}},\"611\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"LinkedIn\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/challahan\"}},\"612\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"GitHub\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.github.com\\/challahan\"}}}}}', '2016-02-08 15:36:43', '2016-02-08 15:36:43', '7a42db0e-ee0a-4348-88e3-b728363f91e1'),
 ('741', '206', '5', '150', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"5\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Behind the Scenes: Making the IdeaBase Promotional Video: Todd Thomson & John Vrhovnik\",\"slug\":\"making-the-ideabase-promotional-video\",\"postDate\":1426084380,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"60\":[\"326\",\"320\"],\"92\":[\"333\"],\"142\":\"\",\"156\":[\"604\",\"605\",\"615\"],\"11\":\"<p>IdeaBase management had a&nbsp;goal: raise awareness about Kent State\\u2019s student-run agency with prospective clients, while telling the stories of the students and staff who work there. Two talented IdeaBase students came together to make that goal a reality \\u2013 with a 4-minute promotional video compiled from&nbsp;interviews with IdeaBase employees.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Todd Thompson&nbsp;and&nbsp;John Vrhovnik&nbsp;are the two students behind the&nbsp;new video.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Todd is an Electronic Media Production major in the School of Journalism and Mass Communication, and John is majoring in Visual Communication Design. Todd was originally hired specifically&nbsp;to work on the promotional video, but he has now joined IdeaBase as an Account Manager and Videographer. John works as a graphic&nbsp;designer. John and Todd explained what it was like working on the video project.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>When asked about their inspiration for the video, both Todd and John looked to a number of existing&nbsp;online videos&nbsp;for ideas. Todd says, \\u201cI already had a vision for the pace and feel I wanted it to have, but John and I looked to&nbsp;Designspiration&nbsp;and&nbsp;Vimeo&nbsp;just for some ideas to move passed any creative walls we hit on the way to completion.\\u201d<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Todd worked specifically on filming, editing, audio production, and directing. John worked on the layout and flow of the graphical content. John was also featured&nbsp;in the video, displaying some of his hand-drawn lettering.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The hardest part of working on the video for John was just getting the project going, while Todd said he struggled at first working with someone from a different major. &nbsp;He also had to&nbsp;change his design process&nbsp;to match John\\u2019s expertise and style of thinking. \\u201cBut, in the end, John taught me so much and he was right all along. His designer\\u2019s mindset has taught me a lot about taking my time with a piece and really mapping things out before making a final decision. John showed me it\\u2019s best to exhaust all options before making a decision, and it truly creates a beautiful product in the end,\\u201d says Todd.<br>John went on to explain, \\u201cwe both had never made something quite like this, and I am incredibly new to video so at the beginning we were just sort of gathering inspiration, building the concepts on paper and mapping out all the content. As soon as we got all the video in, Todd made all the edits, we picked music, started adding type and it all really just came together quite naturally.\\u201d<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Overall, John and Todd felt they learned a lot from each other. Above all,&nbsp;both students think the new video will be a great tool for IdeaBase. \\u201cThis video will benefit IdeaBase by not only improving awareness of what&nbsp;the agency&nbsp;has to offer to students and clients, but it will also help show the types of students that work here and how passionate they are about their careers and how much effort is put into their work here at IdeaBase,\\u201d says Todd.<\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"49\":[\"123\"]}}', '2016-02-08 21:57:07', '2016-02-08 21:57:07', '8520f332-831f-4421-ae51-024d67efc010'),
 ('742', '148', '15', '150', 'en_us', '24', '', '{\"typeId\":\"15\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Work\",\"slug\":\"projects-homepage\",\"postDate\":1453923363,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"590\"],\"71\":\"How we\'re making a difference\",\"72\":\"<p>We make a positive impact on your design and our student designers by taking the time to build right. Read case studies from our past projects to see for yourself.<\\/p>\",\"109\":\"IdeaBase Classroom Experiences\",\"74\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we want our student employees to succeed. That\\u2019s why we partner with Glyphix to teach the next generation through studio experiences. Our students develop and exercise project-based skills in marketing, design, research and more. Additionally, our Responsive Web Design class ensures the next generation of designers and developers understand how to create highly functional and usable websites.<\\/p>\",\"73\":\"Helping our students succeed\",\"148\":\"We\'re not just transforming our clients\' products and brands with our award-winning design solutions; we\'re transforming our student employees by giving them the chance to work directly with clients, managing all stages of design production.\",\"37\":[\"281\"],\"110\":\"See All Work\",\"69\":\"Our Past Work Speaks for Itself\",\"70\":\"<p>We deliver awarding-winning, quality design solutions that transform our clients\\u2019 products and brands. In turn, our talented students get the chance to work directly with clients, developing proposals, managing projects and handling all stages of design production.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-08 21:58:09', '2016-02-08 21:58:09', '61a75c11-5702-493a-a9e6-ccc546eed506'),
