 ('752', '146', '3', '150', 'en_us', '12', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Quintin Steele\",\"slug\":\"quintin-steele\",\"postDate\":1446740340,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Hi, I\'m Quintin Steele (I know, it is a sweet name). I am currently a graduate student in Visual Communication Design at &nbsp;Kent State University and will graduate at the end of&nbsp;summer semester&nbsp;2016.&nbsp;&nbsp;I am a freelance designer, instructor for KSU&nbsp;and creative director at IdeaBase. I watch way too many movies and drink entirely too much coffee. When I was 8, I was the&nbsp;raingutter regatta champion of my CubScout pack. I really enjoy working with others and constantly pushing myself to learn more about everything around me.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"B.F.A. Visual Communication Design, M.F.A. Visual Communication Design Graduate Student \",\"4\":\"qsteele@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Quintin\",\"26\":[\"5\"],\"3\":\"Creative Director, IdeaBase\",\"114\":\"Steele\",\"5\":\"330.672.7300\",\"27\":[\"298\"],\"89\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-09 06:06:33', '2016-02-09 06:06:33', '12c586ad-8ed5-4440-8afd-58e99b10522c'),
 ('753', '119', '3', '150', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Kristin Dowling\",\"slug\":\"kristin-dowling\",\"postDate\":1445536440,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Kristin is the Business Development Manager for IdeaBase (formerly The Tannery). She is responsible for building client relationships in order to provide high quality experiential learning opportunities for our students.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>She previously served as an Entrepreneur-in-Residence for the Center for Entrepreneurship and Business Innovation in the Kent State University College of Business. Her experience prior to coming to Kent State University was as Regional Operations Manager for Kinko\\u2019s Inc. (now known as FedEx Office).&nbsp;Kristin is a proud graduate of Kent State University, with a Bachelor\'s Degree in Business Management.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Business Management\",\"4\":\"kdowling@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Kristin\",\"26\":[\"5\"],\"3\":\"Business Development Manager\",\"114\":\"Dowling\",\"5\":\"330.672.7366\",\"27\":[\"293\"],\"89\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"LinkedIn\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/kristindowling\"}}}}}', '2016-02-09 06:07:40', '2016-02-09 06:07:40', '1867644c-9143-40b0-90a2-c421b0a57b4e'),
 ('754', '234', '3', '150', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Martha Arbogast\",\"slug\":\"martha-arbogast\",\"postDate\":1450378740,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Martha Arbogast is a graphic designer. She spent the past summer in Washington D.C. interning at the Smithsonian National Air and Space Museum as an exhibits design intern. Last year, she worked at the Kent State University Honors College where she produced marketing materials to promote the college and the many programs and events it hosted.&nbsp;Beyond design, Martha loves her dog&nbsp;Ursa and hiking with her fianc\\u00e9 in Cuyahoga Valley National Park.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Visual Communication Design\",\"4\":\"marbogast@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Martha\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Designer\",\"114\":\"Arbogast\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"296\"],\"89\":{\"461\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Martha\'s Portfolio\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.marthaarbogast.com\"}}}}}', '2016-02-09 06:09:22', '2016-02-09 06:09:22', '7e6c0491-c8e3-4f15-bb04-70c906265dfa'),
 ('755', '316', '3', '150', 'en_us', '10', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Callie Sullivan\",\"slug\":\"callie-sullivan\",\"postDate\":1451403540,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Callie received her Bachelor\\u2019s degree in English from UW-Madison and is currently pursuing her Master\\u2019s degree in User Experience Design through Kent State University, where she will graduate in August of 2016.&nbsp;She is dually employed by IdeaBase, as well as a pharmacy benefit management company called Navitus based out of Madison, Wisconsin. At Navitus, Callie works as a Marketing Analyst and is part of the organization\\u2019s Web team, assisting primarily on content creation and organization for both the company\\u2019s internal and external sites. works in the Marketing department of a pharmacy benefit management company called Navitus based out of Madison, Wisconsin. At IdeaBase, Callie has worked on several projects&mdash;including the State Library of Ohio redesign, the design of the ICE Consulting website, and the redesign of the IdeaBase website&mdash;as the lead Content Strategist and Information Architect.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>When Callie\\u2019s not eating, sleeping and breathing UX, she\\u2019s pursuing her other passions, which include music, the French language, travel and cheese plates.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"B.A. English, M.S. User Experience Design Graduate Student\",\"4\":\"csullivan@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Callie \",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"User Experience Designer\",\"114\":\"Sullivan\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"506\"],\"89\":{\"443\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Facebook\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/calliesheasullivan\"}},\"444\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Twitter\",\"staf