 ('757', '149', '3', '204', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Larrie King\",\"slug\":\"larrie-king\",\"postDate\":1447175700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Larrie King joined the faulty of the School of Visual Communication Design in 2014 after graduating from the program with an MFA. He also holds a BFA and an MA in design from Northwestern State University, where he taught in the design program prior to attending Kent State. Originally from Louisiana, Larrie\\u2019s creative career began in fine art. Along with teaching and practicing as a freelance designer over the years, he has also exhibited work as a painter and illustrator.<br>Larrie\\u2019s areas of expertise include print design, identity development and branding design, and research. He recently presented research from his graduate studies at the 9th Annual International Design Principles and Practiced Conference, and continues to work with global organizations like Lifewater International.<br>As Creative Director of the award-winning Glyphix Studio, Larrie works closely with the School of VCD\\u2019s top performing students, guiding them to create design solutions for organizations like The Veale Foundation, Portage Parks District, Schneller, and Kent State University. He also serves as the school\\u2019s internship coordinator, forging relationships with local and regional studios and business owners who provide our students with competitive internship and employment opportunities.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"MFA in Visual Communication Design, Kent State University, MA in Design, Northwestern State University, BFA in Design, Northwestern State University\",\"4\":\"lking@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Larrie\",\"26\":[\"5\"],\"3\":\"Creative Director, Glyphix\",\"114\":\"King\",\"5\":\"330.672.7300\",\"27\":[\"242\"],\"89\":{\"738\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Behance\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.behance.net\\/larrieking\\/wip\"}},\"739\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Website\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/www.larrieking.com\"}},\"740\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"LinkedIn\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/larrie-king-39580654\"}}}}}', '2016-02-09 15:23:24', '2016-02-09 15:23:24', '4663d291-8298-4ba1-b9de-2fa27683f909'),
 ('758', '743', '3', '204', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Dylan Palchesko\",\"slug\":\"dylan-palchesko\",\"postDate\":1455032079,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"\",\"77\":\"Advertising\",\"4\":\"dpalchesko@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Dylan\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Account Manager\",\"114\":\"Palchesko\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"742\"],\"89\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-09 15:34:39', '2016-02-09 15:34:39', 'a7254cdb-e7fa-4fea-8d1a-770cc1a70593'),
 ('759', '426', '3', '204', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Francesca Demming\",\"slug\":\"francesca-demming\",\"postDate\":1452274920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Francesca Demming is a sophomore majoring in public relations at Kent State University expecting to graduate in the fall of 2018.&nbsp;She is involved in PRSSA and UNICEF and is considering a minor in non-profit studies. Francesca currently has an internship at the School of Library and Information Science where she writes press releases, works on social media, and manages content for the Museum Studies program as well as the Health Informatics program. She loves rescuing animals and works part time at an animal hospital. She has a dog named Buddy, two cats named Bandit and Lou-Lou and a horse named Dakota. Francesca hopes to combine her love of animals and public relations by working in a non-profit animal rescue in the future.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Public Relations\",\"4\":\"fdemming@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Francesca\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Account Manager\",\"114\":\"Demming\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":\"\",\"89\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Twitter\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/FrancescaKSU\"}}}}}', '2016-02-09 15:41:06', '2016-02-09 15:41:06', '29301eec-7a28-4b99-b04f-4da8ce60123a'),
 ('760', '319', '3', '204', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Grace Jacobsen\",\"slug\":\"grace-jacobsen\",\"postDate\":1451404260,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Grace is&nbsp;from Cincinnati, Ohio but Kent has become her&nbsp;second home. Art and drawing have been lifelong passions of hers&nbsp;and when she&nbsp;had to decide what she&nbsp;wanted to do at school, Grace&nbsp;looked for a way to bring what she&nbsp;loved into her&nbsp;career. Some of her&nbsp;life goals include getting a fun job and petting as many dogs as she&nbsp;can.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Visual Communication Design\",\"4\":\"gjacobsen@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Grace\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Designer\",\"114\":\"Jacobsen\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":\"\",\"89\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Grace\'s Portfolio\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/gracejacobsen.myportfolio.com\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Behance\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.behance.net\\/Grace_Jacobsen\"}}}}}', '2016-02-09 15:44:20', '2016-02-09 15:44:20', 'd4f996f1-dff4-4950-8059-1f93c96fa943');
