 ('767', '236', '3', '204', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Sarah Holzer\",\"slug\":\"sarah-holzer\",\"postDate\":1450378740,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Sarah&nbsp;loves all things creative.&nbsp;Originally from Pittsburgh,&nbsp;Sarah&nbsp;currently reside in Ohio while working towards her&nbsp;BFA degree in Visual Communication Design from Kent State University, where she\'s&nbsp;graduating&nbsp;in May of 2016.&nbsp;When Sarah is&nbsp;not rattling her&nbsp;brain&nbsp;creatively solving a problem she enjoys,&nbsp;yoga, the outdoors, cooking (although sometimes the fire alarm is&nbsp;her&nbsp;kitchen timer), hanging out with her&nbsp;dog&nbsp;and Elvis.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Visual Communication Design\",\"4\":\"sholzer@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Sarah\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Designer\",\"114\":\"Holzer\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"302\"],\"89\":{\"457\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Sarah\'s Portfolio \",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/sarahholzer.com\\/\"}}}}}', '2016-02-09 16:12:46', '2016-02-09 16:12:46', 'd50bed9f-3e2a-469d-a593-da50eb9ac531'),
 ('768', '319', '3', '204', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"Grace Jacobsen\",\"slug\":\"grace-jacobsen\",\"postDate\":1451404260,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Grace is&nbsp;from Cincinnati, Ohio but Kent has become her&nbsp;second home. Art and drawing have been lifelong passions of hers&nbsp;and when she&nbsp;had to decide what she&nbsp;wanted to do at school, Grace&nbsp;looked for a way to bring what she&nbsp;loved into her&nbsp;career. Some of her&nbsp;life goals include getting a fun job and petting as many dogs as she&nbsp;can.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Visual Communication Design\",\"4\":\"gjacobsen@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Grace\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Designer\",\"114\":\"Jacobsen\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"748\"],\"89\":{\"745\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Grace\'s Portfolio\",\"staffSocLink\":\"http:\\/\\/gracejacobsen.myportfolio.com\"}},\"746\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Behance\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.behance.net\\/Grace_Jacobsen\"}}}}}', '2016-02-09 16:25:07', '2016-02-09 16:25:07', '876d801e-230a-4dca-98b3-c41ae959d030'),
 ('769', '147', '3', '204', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Victoria Ripepi\",\"slug\":\"victoria-ripepi\",\"postDate\":1446762360,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"118\":\"\",\"6\":\"<p>Victoria Ripepi is a&nbsp;5th year senior graduating in May 2016,&nbsp;majoring in Communication Studies, concentration interpersonal. Victoria is from Hudson, OH and came to Kent State because she&nbsp;is&nbsp;the oldest of 6 kids and didn\'t want to be far away from home. After being here for 5 years, she&nbsp;is&nbsp;very ready to move onto the next chapter of her&nbsp;life and begin finding a job outside of&nbsp;Ohio. She&nbsp;is&nbsp;the event coordinator at IdeaBase and helped successfully plan&nbsp;an Open House in the Fall of 2015 that was attended by over 100 people.&nbsp;Now Victoria&nbsp;will be joining IdeaBase this Spring 2016 as an Account Manager and she\'s&nbsp;very excited for that. She&nbsp;hopes to get a job in corporate event planning and\\/or an experience marketing firm. Previous to working at IdeaBase, Victoria&nbsp;worked for a small event planning company that put on 100 vendor art and craft shows throughout Northeast Ohio and the Columbus area. She&nbsp;is&nbsp;a people person and always haves a smile on her&nbsp;face.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Victoria&nbsp;has&nbsp;two&nbsp;cats, favorite color is black and&nbsp;favorite food is fried pickles.<\\/p>\",\"77\":\"Communication Studies and Interpersonal concentration\",\"4\":\"vripepi@ideabasekent.com\",\"148\":\"\",\"115\":\"Victoria\",\"26\":[\"6\"],\"3\":\"Event Coordinator\",\"114\":\"Ripepi\",\"5\":\"\",\"27\":[\"307\"],\"89\":{\"507\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"Linkedin\",\"staffSocLink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/victoriaripepi\"}},\"508\":{\"type\":\"staffSocName\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"staffSocName\":\"\",\"staffSocLink\":\"\"}}}}}', '2016-02-09 16:33:14', '2016-02-09 16:33: