 ('928', '414', '4', '150', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Summa Diversity Report\",\"slug\":\"summa-diversity-report\",\"postDate\":1452028500,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"428\"],\"61\":[\"146\",\"213\",\"325\",\"424\"],\"9\":\"<p>The Summa Diversity Report was a&nbsp;multifaceted learning opportunity for all of the&nbsp;IdeaBase team. Students discovered&nbsp;how to work within brand standards and&nbsp;formulating project strategies, pushing them to produce&nbsp;some of their&nbsp;highest quality of work. The in-person, interactive collaboration the team received from the client was inspiring, and motivational. The final project was an excellent example of team work culminating in a captivating, informative, creative piece of design. &nbsp;<br><\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"161\":\"1\",\"46\":[\"593\",\"668\",\"653\",\"667\",\"659\",\"655\",\"665\",\"664\",\"660\",\"663\",\"658\",\"662\",\"657\",\"656\",\"654\"],\"88\":[\"179\"],\"104\":\"\",\"162\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-11 22:43:48', '2016-02-11 22:43:48', 'b5c38223-1075-42df-b039-aad695204c93'),
 ('929', '414', '4', '150', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Summa Diversity Report\",\"slug\":\"summa-diversity-report\",\"postDate\":1452028500,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"117\":[\"428\"],\"61\":[\"146\",\"213\",\"325\",\"424\"],\"9\":\"<p>The Summa Diversity Report was a&nbsp;multifaceted learning opportunity for all of the&nbsp;IdeaBase team. Students discovered&nbsp;how to work within brand standards and&nbsp;formulating project strategies, pushing them to produce&nbsp;some of their&nbsp;highest quality of work. The in-person, interactive collaboration the team received from the client was inspiring, and motivational. The final project was an excellent example of team work culminating in a captivating, informative, creative piece of design. &nbsp;<br><\\/p>\",\"148\":\"\",\"161\":\"1\",\"46\":[\"662\",\"593\",\"668\",\"653\",\"667\",\"659\",\"655\",\"665\",\"664\",\"660\",\"663\",\"658\",\"657\",\"656\",\"654\"],\"88\":[\"179\"],\"104\":\"\",\"162\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-11 22:44:25', '2016-02-11 22:44:25', 'ce5c81f7-c8ee-4cdd-bd74-11fdf202d838'),
 ('930', '515', '14', '150', 'en_us', '36', '', '{\"typeId\":\"14\",\"authorId\":\"204\",\"title\":\"User Experience Testing Lab\",\"slug\":\"ux\",\"postDate\":1453822920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"120\":{\"517\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Eye Tracking Usability<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer both traditional desktop eye tracking as well as wearable eye&nbsp;tracking technologies from Tobii. Eye tracking allows our user experience designers to closely study your product to see exactly where users are (and aren\\u2019t) looking. Using this measurable data, we\\u2019re able to suggest user experience improvements that help your users complete their goals faster and easier. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our eye tracking software can produce stunning visualizations, including heat maps and gaze plots, to help you communicate your findings to your stakeholders. It\\u2019s also a great tool for academic research. In fact, IdeaBase was featured in a <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.rjionline.org\\/news\\/eyes-have-it\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">national study on multimedia journalism<\\/a> by the Reynolds Journalism Institute.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Introducing Tobii Glasses 2<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>For the first time, we\\u2019re able to accurately conduct testing on mobile devices, including phones and tablets, and environmental designs, such as store displays and product packaging using the state of the art Tobii Glasses 2.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\"}},\"553\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"\"}},\"552\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"564\"]}},\"518\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>In-Person and Remote Usability Testing<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We offer task-based usability studies that are conducted in-person by our research team. &nbsp;We\\u2019re also able to conduct remote user research using a variety of online tools. &nbsp;Our team can assist with recruiting, writing testing scripts and analyzing testing results.<\\/p>\"}},\"600\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"843\"]}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"basicPageText\":\"<h2>Open Device Testing Lab<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With a variety of mobile devices on the market, it\\u2019s critical that your website or app translates across platforms and offers a consistent user experience. That\\u2019s where our Open Device Lab comes in. &nbsp;With on-site access to many&nbsp;of the most popular devices (and expanding), our lab is a great place to test for bugs and implement fixes.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Partnering with Open Device Lab, our&nbsp;clients can now schedule a time to use our device lab at no charge!<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We currently offer access to the following devices:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Apple iPhone 4<\\/li><li>Apple iPhone 5<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy S4<\\/li><li>Samsung Galaxy Tab<\\/li><li>Apple iPad 2<\\/li><li>Toshiba Windows Laptop<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you\'d like to come in and use the lab, just contact us by email, phone or via the form below. Have an old device that you\\u2019re no longer using? Donate it to our non-profit agency using this form.<\\/p>\"}},\"537\":{\"type\":\"button\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"buttonTitle\":\"Donate a Device\",\"buttonUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/opendevicelab.com\\/DYDD\"}}},\"148\":\"Our on-site UX Testing Lab offers clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. We offer usability testing, Tobii eyetracking, and testing across a variety of mobile devices to ensure cross-platform functionality.\",\"37\":[\"842\"],\"135\":\"<p>We proudly manage our own in-house User Experience Testing Lab. This on-site lab complements our design services by offering clients the ability to test their products using our advanced research equipment. The lab is operated by an experienced User Experience Designer and a team of graduate students from Kent State\\u2019s renowned User Experience Design master\\u2019s program.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-11 22:45:40', '2016-02-11 22:45:40', '19385af5-62bb-4c5b-8726-0d4950478443'),
 ('931', '109', '12', '150', 'en_us', '34', '', '{\"typeId\":\"12\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Services\",\"slug\":\"process-index\",\"postDate\":1453923350,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"591\"],\"148\":\"Let our suite of user research, design and testing services guide your product development; we offer everything from competitive analysis to graphic and Web design to eyetracking and usability testing in our very own UX Testing Lab.\",\"37\":[\"829\"],\"106\":\"<p>While our unique business model allows us to deliver high-quality products at an affordable cost, there\\u2019s no \\u201cone size fits all\\u201d when it comes to individual client needs. We work with our clients upfront to define goals and timelines to ensure that we deliver a great end&nbsp;product within the project\\u2019s constraints. Together, we\\u2019ll plan and build something great, and it won\\u2019t break the bank.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Contact us today and we\'ll put together a customized proposal&nbsp;for your next project.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"107\":\"Sounds great, how much does it cost?\",\"79\":\"<p>We support our clients\\u2019 design initiatives from the early discovery phase through implementation (or anywhere in between). Whether you\\u2019re laying the foundation for your product\\u2019s success, or building out and refining your design, we\\u2019re here to help. And we do all of this right here locally from our <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ideabasekent.com\\/prod\\/about#entry:492:url\\\">fabulous office space<\\/a> in downtown Kent.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"42\":\"Our design services are tailored to you\",\"94\":{\"183\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Discover\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Discover who your users are and what they are looking for in your product.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"User Interviews\"},{\"col1\":\"Surveys\"},{\"col1\":\"Competitive Analysis\"},{\"col1\":\"Persona Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Focus Groups\"},{\"col1\":\"Heuristics \"}],\"icon1\":[\"252\"],\"icon2\":[\"253\"],\"icon3\":[\"248\"],\"icon4\":[\"257\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"245\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our targeted user research methods empower you to more effectively address your users\'&nbsp;needs.<\\/p>\"}},\"184\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Design\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Design a creative product that delivers on user and business needs.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"Print & Graphic Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Video Production\"},{\"col1\":\"Email Marketing\"},{\"col1\":\"Web Design & Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Content Strategy\"},{\"col1\":\"Environmental Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Brand Identity \"},{\"col1\":\"Social Media Campaigns\"}],\"icon1\":[\"249\"],\"icon2\":[\"254\"],\"icon3\":[\"256\"],\"icon4\":[\"246\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"244\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our design strategies, whether through print, video or web, deliver custom solutions that&nbsp;promote both business and customer needs.<\\/p>\"}},\"185\":{\"type\":\"processMatrix\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"homeProcessName\":\"Refine\",\"homeProcessDescription\":\"<p>Refine an existing product with our advanced testing process.<\\/p>\",\"homeProcessExampleTable\":[{\"col1\":\"In-Person Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Remote Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Device & Performance Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Eyetracking Usability \"}],\"icon1\":[\"247\"],\"icon2\":[\"250\"],\"icon3\":[\"251\"],\"icon4\":[\"255\"],\"homepageIcon\":[\"258\"],\"homepageDescription\":\"<p>Our advanced usability testing tools, including eye tracking, allow you to evaluate the effectiveness of design solutions.<\\/p>\"}}},\"108\":\"More about our UX Testing Lab\",\"80\":\"<p>We can test the performance and usability of your product on various devices in our User Experience Testing Lab. This is a great resource to ensure that your product translates across all platforms.\\r\\n<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-11 22:46:45', '2016-02-11 22:46:45', '1df9cb79-846f-4888-80fa-65e6771e39ba'),
