 ('963', '148', '15', '150', 'en_us', '27', '', '{\"typeId\":\"15\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Work\",\"slug\":\"projects-homepage\",\"postDate\":1453923363,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"155\":[\"590\"],\"71\":\"How we\'re making a difference\",\"72\":\"<p>We make a positive impact on your design and our student designers by taking the time to build right. Read case studies from our past projects to see for yourself.<\\/p>\",\"109\":\"IdeaBase Classroom Experiences\",\"74\":\"<p>At IdeaBase, we want our student employees to succeed. That\\u2019s why we partner with Glyphix to teach the next generation through studio experiences. Our students develop and exercise project-based skills in marketing, design, research and more. Additionally, our Responsive Web Design class ensures the next generation of designers and developers understand how to create highly functional and usable websites.<\\/p>\",\"73\":\"Helping our students succeed\",\"148\":\"We\'re not just transforming our clients\' products and brands with our award-winning design solutions; we\'re transforming our student employees by giving them the chance to work directly with clients, managing all stages of design production.\",\"37\":[\"833\"],\"110\":\"See All Work\",\"69\":\"Work That Speaks for Itself\",\"70\":\"<p>We deliver awarding-winning, quality design solutions that transform our clients\\u2019 products and brands. In turn, our talented students get the chance to work directly with clients, developing proposals, managing projects and handling all stages of design production.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-02-12 17:48:48', '2016-02-12 17:48:48', 'f9c1843b-57d0-4a83-946c-0608ab5705e6'),
