 ('18', '517', 'en_us', '<h2>Eye Tracking Usability</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer both traditional desktop eye tracking as well as wearable eye&nbsp;tracking technologies from Tobii. Eye tracking allows our user experience designers to closely study your product to see exactly where users are (and arent) looking. Using this measurable data, were able to suggest user experience improvements that help your users complete their goals faster and easier. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Our eye tracking software can produce stunning visualizations, including heat maps and gaze plots, to help you communicate your findings to your stakeholders. Its also a great tool for academic research. In fact, IdeaBase was featured in a <a href=\"http://www.rjionline.org/news/eyes-have-it\" target=\"_blank\">national study on multimedia journalism</a> by the Reynolds Journalism Institute.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Introducing Tobii Glasses 2</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>For the first time, were able to accurately conduct testing on mobile devices, including phones and tablets, and environmental designs, such as store displays and product packaging using the state of the art Tobii Glasses 2.&nbsp;<br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-26 15:42:46', '2016-02-11 22:45:40', '453b4046-3885-49b5-8f85-b1167b90a741'),
 ('19', '518', 'en_us', '<h2>In-Person and Remote Usability Testing</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer task-based usability studies that are conducted in-person by our research team. &nbsp;Were also able to conduct remote user research using a variety of online tools. &nbsp;Our team can assist with recruiting, writing testing scripts and analyzing testing results.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-26 15:42:46', '2016-02-11 22:45:40', 'b357ef86-a4ae-4b9d-abd3-1161fd38cf59'),
 ('20', '519', 'en_us', '<h2>Open Device Testing Lab</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With a variety of mobile devices on the market, its critical that your website or app translates across platforms and offers a consistent user experience. Thats where our Open Device Lab comes in. &nbsp;With on-site access to many&nbsp;of the most popular devices (and expanding), our lab is a great place to test for bugs and implement fixes.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Partnering with Open Device Lab, our&nbsp;clients can now schedule a time to use our device lab at no charge!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>We currently offer access to the following devices:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Apple iPhone 4</li><li>Apple iPhone 5</li><li>Samsung Galaxy S4</li><li>Samsung Galaxy Tab</li><li>Apple iPad 2</li><li>Toshiba Windows Laptop</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>If you\'d like to come in and use the lab, just contact us by email, phone or via the form below. Have an old device that youre no longer using? Donate it to our non-profit agency using this form.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-26 15:42:46', '2016-02-11 22:45:40', '2d94a811-e904-459b-8346-714488031b2a'),
 ('25', '525', 'en_us', '<h2>Qualifications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our student employees come from a variety of backgrounds and benefit from our comprehensive service offering. Our student employees are:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Part-time or full-time Kent State University students</li><li>Taking at least 6 credit hours</li><li>Passionate about design</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-26 16:18:19', '2016-02-11 22:39:27', '3215036f-9eb5-41f7-ac7d-dde72208fbe0'),
 ('29', '533', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VqQZbh8P8AI', ' In this IdeaBase student-produced video, our students talk about their experiences working at IdeaBase.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-26 16:48:34', '2016-02-09 21:25:51', '053eca16-1fa2-44d7-a192-78331e983ba9'),
 ('30', '534', 'en_us', '<h2>IN THE HEART OF DOWNTOWN KENT</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our office space&mdash;conveniently located in Downtown Kent&mdash;features an open layout with a conference room, creative workspace, educational area and <a href=\"{entry:515:url}\">UX Testing Lab</a>; its a great space for collaboration for students and clients alike!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-26 16:48:34', '2016-02-09 21:25:51', 'f878f9b1-b5ef-493f-bad6-3e7b63bfd92f'),
 ('31', '535', 'en_us', NULL, 'Visit us today!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-26 16:48:34', '2016-02-09 21:25:51', '516bd8a8-352b-4459-9f6c-c3644b385203'),
 ('32', '536', 'en_us', '<h2>A LEGACY OF STUDENT-LED DESIGN SOLUTIONS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Formerly the Tannery, IdeaBase opened in 2009 as the brainchild of Jim Gaudino, the founding dean of the <a href=\"http://www.kent.edu/cci\" target=\"_blank\">College of Communication and Information (CCI)</a>. Gaudino worked with the directors from each of the CCI schools to develop a vision for a student-staffed organization where students could receive hands-on experience. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>In 2014, to better reflect its core mission of providing unique educational experiences while delivering quality design solutions, the Tannery transformed into IdeaBase. Within the same year, IdeaBase expanded its service offering with the addition of <a href=\"http://www.kent.edu/glyphix\" target=\"_blank\">Glyphix</a>, a classroom studio experience from the <a href=\"http://www.kent.edu/vcd\">School of Visual Communication Design</a>. IdeaBase continues to operate as part of the CCI, always evolving to bring new services and experiences to the university community and beyond.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-26 16:48:34', '2016-02-09 21:25:51', '54712ae9-7589-45c0-a14a-416a30bfa564'),
 ('33', '537', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, 'Donate a Device', 'http://opendevicelab.com/DYDD', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-26 16:48:36', '2016-02-11 22:45:40', 'b8125212-ba0d-4eee-91d6-0cff25f97c45'),
 ('35', '544', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, 'Learn more about Glyphix', 'http://www.kent.edu/glyphix', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-28 14:54:26', '2016-02-04 16:50:52', 'ec87dae8-8d9c-478e-bdb5-8c70f09708a1'),
 ('36', '545', 'en_us', '<h2>Responsive Web Design&nbsp;Courses & Workshops</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Designed with the goal of bringing together students from multiple disciplines from within the <a href=\"http://www.kent.edu/cci\">College of Communication and Information</a>, the Responsive Web Design (RWD) courses offered through Kent State give students the skills they need to become web designers. Hands-on classes encourage active learning, and course material is constantly evolving, integrating the latest advancements in design, development and user experience design.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-28 14:54:26', '2016-02-04 16:50:52', '84ba5865-ce57-495c-ba87-a7422d91fcc4'),
 ('37', '546', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, 'Learn more about RWD', 'http://rwdkent.com/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-28 14:54:26', '2016-02-04 16:50:52', '2f4c5002-c909-4bfd-bb2a-1459bbcb15f9'),
 ('38', '547', 'en_us', '<h2>Glyphix</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As the&nbsp;most renowned&nbsp;member of the IdeaBase family and one of the first programs of its kind, <a href=\"http://www.kent.edu/glyphix\">Glyphix</a> offers student designers the opportunity to develop creative solutions for real-world design projects. As a Glyphix designer, students gain course credits toward graduation, as well as valuable experience in teamwork, design generation and client engagement. Glyphix is located in Downtown Kent and is part of the School of Visual Communication Design. &nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-28 14:57:50', '2016-02-04 16:50:51', '468c80d6-ec5d-4d13-a9f1-6bc12a89178c'),
 ('39', '549', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-28 15:13:06', '2016-02-04 16:50:51', 'd647b3a7-a6a8-4ab8-bec8-f339181f3258'),
