 ('45', '555', 'en_us', '<h2>Degree Programs</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our students are primarily from the College of Communication and Information, but we have team members from other majors as well. &nbsp;Some of our past student majors include:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Visual Communication</li><li>Design</li><li>Communication Studies</li><li>Advertising</li><li>Public Relations</li><li>Journalism</li><li>Computer Information Systems</li><li>Computer Science</li><li>User Experience Design</li><li>Library & Information Science</li><li>Digital Sciences</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Positions</h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>We offer students the chance to work with students from a variety of backgrounds and disciplines. &nbsp;Just a few of the student positions at IdeaBase include:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Account&nbsp;Manager</li><li>Designer</li><li>Front-End Web Designer</li><li>Back-End&nbsp;Web Developer</li><li>Copywriter</li><li>Videographer</li><li>Accountant</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-28 15:19:26', '2016-02-11 22:39:27', '4dd47f4a-2bfb-4261-9a8e-8d2c40b446c4'),
 ('46', '558', 'en_us', '<h2>Once You\'ve Arrived</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Feel free to use either of our two entrances. Once youve arrived, go up the stairs or take the elevator to the second floor and youll find our office.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Our <strong>front entrance</strong> is next to 4 Cats Art Studio and our <strong>back entrance</strong> is behind Tree City Coffee and beside Flashers Cleaners.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Need help finding our office? Give us a call at 330-672-7300.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-28 15:31:46', '2016-02-10 02:40:50', '4de3301c-4b02-4a6f-8d9f-d2d5dc8a68d9'),
 ('48', '561', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-28 15:39:25', '2016-02-10 02:40:50', 'e8d86984-692f-4a40-8ba9-c7bd9e4da6e3'),
 ('49', '562', 'en_us', '<h2>Parking</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>IdeaBase parking options are listed below. &nbsp;Parking is the&nbsp;most difficult to find&nbsp;during lunch hours and close to 5 p.m. &nbsp;If you are parking on the Kent State campus, we\'re about a 10 minute walk down the Lefton Esplanade.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-28 15:49:55', '2016-02-10 02:40:50', '56ffb607-3e0a-48d0-bc7f-70f0f3376da3'),
 ('50', '594', 'en_us', '<h2>DELIVERING MEANINGFUL DESIGN SOLUTIONS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the diverse talent of our student employees, we offer a comprehensive service offering that includes advertising, branding, copywriting, identity design, marketing research, Web design, usability studies, environmental design services and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ideabasekent.com/new/dev/prototype/templates/process.php\"></a><a href=\"{entry:109:url}\">much more</a>. As part of a thriving university community, we also have access to additional resources to enhance our suite of services.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-04 16:28:06', '2016-02-09 21:25:51', '169267f5-bf4e-49b4-8bcd-ae4337d5cfcc'),
 ('52', '597', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Apply for a Job', '<p>Think youll be a great fit? &nbsp;Email your resume to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@ideabasekent.com\">info@ideabasekent.com</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not a student? Not a problem&mdash;you can still get involved by mentoring students, donating supplies or joining our professional advisory board. &nbsp;Contact&nbsp;<a href=\"{entry:119:url}\">Kristin Dowling</a>, Business Development Manager, today.</p>', '2016-02-04 17:10:57', '2016-02-11 22:39:27', '56fe900c-3d03-4503-99dc-06a32e33a79c'),
 ('53', '600', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-04 17:23:45', '2016-02-11 22:45:40', 'fedd1cb4-7a6d-4531-828a-a0413a1ebfc4'),
