 ('1', '183', 'en_us', 'Discover', '<p>Discover who your users are and what they are looking for in your product.</p>', '[{\"col1\":\"User Interviews\"},{\"col1\":\"Surveys\"},{\"col1\":\"Competitive Analysis\"},{\"col1\":\"Persona Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Focus Groups\"},{\"col1\":\"Heuristics \"}]', '<p>Our targeted user research methods empower you to more effectively address your users\'&nbsp;needs.</p>', '2015-12-03 20:37:02', '2016-02-12 17:47:42', '34ba40c8-2114-43cd-81fb-ae3e4242c316'),
 ('2', '184', 'en_us', 'Design', '<p>Design a creative product that delivers on user and business needs.</p>', '[{\"col1\":\"Print & Graphic Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Video Production\"},{\"col1\":\"Email Marketing\"},{\"col1\":\"Web Design & Development\"},{\"col1\":\"Content Strategy\"},{\"col1\":\"Environmental Design\"},{\"col1\":\"Brand Identity \"},{\"col1\":\"Social Media Campaigns\"}]', '<p>Our design strategies, whether through print, video or web, deliver custom solutions that&nbsp;promote both business and customer needs.</p>', '2015-12-03 20:37:02', '2016-02-12 17:47:42', '67d6dacf-d5e2-4f71-9f6b-6501e3bb425c'),
 ('3', '185', 'en_us', 'Refine', '<p>Refine an existing product with our advanced testing process.</p>', '[{\"col1\":\"In-Person Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Remote Usability Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Device & Performance Testing\"},{\"col1\":\"Eyetracking Usability \"}]', '<p>Our advanced usability testing tools, including eye tracking, allow you to evaluate the effectiveness of design solutions.</p>', '2015-12-03 20:37:02', '2016-02-12 17:47:42', '98bbf713-2526-45e0-b148-299d6113589c');
