 ('120', 'field', '6', 'en_us', ' chris is a full time user experience designer for ideabase and kent state university s college of communication and information he manages user research usability and interactive web projects at ideabase and works one on one with ideabase students to teach them web design user experience and content strategy techniques he also teaches a class on responsive web design as well as a class on human computer interaction for digital sciences his areas of study include responsive web design usability information architecture and content management system design '),
