 ('492', 'field', '120', 'en_us', ' delivering meaningful design solutions thanks to the diverse talent of our student employees we offer a comprehensive service offering that includes advertising branding copywriting identity design marketing research web design usability studies environmental design services and much more as part of a thriving university community we also have access to additional resources to enhance our suite of services in this ideabase student produced video our students talk about their experiences working at ideabase https www youtube com watch v=vqqzbh8p8ai in the heart of downtown kent our office spaceconveniently located in downtown kentfeatures an open layout with a conference room creative workspace educational area and ux testing lab it s a great space for collaboration for students and clients alike directions and parking visit us today our office as seen from east main street a legacy of student led design solutions formerly the tannery ideabase opened in 2009 as the brainchild of jim gaudino the founding dean of the college of communication and information cci gaudino worked with the directors from each of the cci schools to develop a vision for a student staffed organization where students could receive hands on experience in 2014 to better reflect its core mission of providing unique educational experiences while delivering quality design solutions the tannery transformed into ideabase within the same year ideabase expanded its service offering with the addition of glyphix a classroom studio experience from the school of visual communication design ideabase continues to operate as part of the cci always evolving to bring new services and experiences to the university community and beyond people learn more about our team '),
